1
00:00:00,467 --> 00:00:02,435
(Their ages were finally revealed.)

2
00:00:02,736 --> 00:00:03,536
I was...

3
00:00:04,638 --> 00:00:06,405
born in 2002.

4
00:00:06,874 --> 00:00:09,108
(Si Won, 25)

5
00:00:10,410 --> 00:00:12,978
(Si Won is 12 years younger than Yu Jin.)

6
00:00:13,347 --> 00:00:15,281
I was born in 1992.

7
00:00:15,282 --> 00:00:16,950
(Ju Hee, 35 years old)

8
00:00:16,951 --> 00:00:19,185
(She's 11 years older than Yun So.)

9
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:21,520
So she's 35.

10
00:00:22,723 --> 00:00:24,791
You don't have to answer
if you feel pressured.

11
00:00:24,992 --> 00:00:26,626
Do I still have a chance?

12
00:00:26,627 --> 00:00:27,760
For you?

13
00:00:27,761 --> 00:00:29,829
(Nodding)

14
00:00:30,230 --> 00:00:32,231
After yesterday's date,

15
00:00:33,534 --> 00:00:35,568
I've been thinking a lot about you.

16
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:37,803
Have I always been your favorite?

17
00:00:37,804 --> 00:00:39,938
Is that why you were so shocked?

18
00:00:39,939 --> 00:00:42,808
Since yesterday, yes.

19
00:00:42,910 --> 00:00:45,011
Actually, I wrote down your name yesterday
as my first choice.

20
00:00:45,012 --> 00:00:46,179
- Is that so?
- Yes.

21
00:00:46,747 --> 00:00:49,415
I've been wanting
to have a conversation with you.

22
00:00:49,416 --> 00:00:53,119
I think I've become
more interested in you.

23
00:00:53,654 --> 00:00:57,423
(Yu Jin and Si Won learn
how they feel about each other.)

24
00:00:57,592 --> 00:00:59,559
I don't know what you think.

25
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:03,095
I felt like my conversation
with Si Won went better than I expected.

26
00:01:03,096 --> 00:01:05,631
- After only a few hours?
- Yes.

27
00:01:05,632 --> 00:01:07,467
So you've set your heart on Si Won now?

28
00:01:07,468 --> 00:01:10,503
Yes. I think I have.

29
00:01:11,238 --> 00:01:13,239
Actually, I was...

30
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:15,074
a little surprised last night
when you told me that.

31
00:01:15,209 --> 00:01:17,410
You felt a little...

32
00:01:18,378 --> 00:01:20,279
I'm not saying you were aggressive, but...

33
00:01:20,714 --> 00:01:22,148
it felt like a declaration of war.

34
00:01:22,149 --> 00:01:23,617
That was the impression I got.

35
00:01:24,451 --> 00:01:28,120
(Ji Seung felt
like it was a declaration of war.)

36
00:01:28,121 --> 00:01:30,823
I was just trying to explain my situation.

37
00:01:30,824 --> 00:01:32,892
It wasn't a declaration of anything.

38
00:01:32,893 --> 00:01:36,762
(Where will Si Won's heart go?)

39
00:01:36,763 --> 00:01:39,899
Last week, the ages we had
all been the most curious about...

40
00:01:40,634 --> 00:01:43,169
were finally revealed at Yeon House.

41
00:01:43,170 --> 00:01:46,305
For me, this season is my first
as a panelist.

42
00:01:46,607 --> 00:01:47,941
I didn't know how big...

43
00:01:47,942 --> 00:01:50,577
of an aftermath
that information could bring.

44
00:01:50,644 --> 00:01:51,777
What do you think?

45
00:01:52,513 --> 00:01:53,213
It's huge.

46
00:01:53,214 --> 00:01:53,980
- It is.
- I mean...

47
00:01:53,981 --> 00:01:55,682
I realized...

48
00:01:55,849 --> 00:01:58,984
that age can change how people feel...

49
00:01:58,985 --> 00:02:00,453
about each other.

50
00:02:01,255 --> 00:02:05,358
And there are some people
who don't care about it at all.

51
00:02:05,825 --> 00:02:06,859
So it made it even harder...

52
00:02:07,127 --> 00:02:09,228
for me to predict what will happen next.

53
00:02:09,229 --> 00:02:10,563
- Right.
- It's impossible to predict.

54
00:02:12,032 --> 00:02:12,865
What?

55
00:02:14,234 --> 00:02:15,401
(A message for another new day arrives.)

56
00:02:15,602 --> 00:02:16,402
What could it be?

57
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:19,071
- Gosh. This is driving me crazy.
- This is insane.

58
00:02:19,973 --> 00:02:21,607
- What? A group date?
- "A 2-on-2 group date."

59
00:02:21,608 --> 00:02:22,675
"A group date?"

60
00:02:22,676 --> 00:02:24,276
How are they going to pair up?

61
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:27,747
My goodness. We have a group date today.

62
00:02:29,082 --> 00:02:30,949
(A mysterious box...)

63
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:33,552
(appears in the Secret Room.)

64
00:02:33,787 --> 00:02:36,235
(The group date will be
decided by random draw,)

65
00:02:36,236 --> 00:02:38,624
(splitting them into either a group
of 6 or a group of 4.)

66
00:02:38,992 --> 00:02:41,727
"A retro date versus a Gen-Z date."

67
00:02:41,995 --> 00:02:43,762
So it has a theme.

68
00:02:44,431 --> 00:02:46,699
I was hoping to go out...

69
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,768
with Yun So.

70
00:02:48,869 --> 00:02:50,136
Ju Hee has changed.

71
00:02:50,938 --> 00:02:53,573
I wanted to get to know the people...

72
00:02:53,574 --> 00:02:54,774
I was attracted to.

73
00:02:55,976 --> 00:02:57,710
I want to go out with Jung Won
as much as possible.

74
00:02:58,412 --> 00:03:02,215
I was hoping to be grouped with Jung Won.

75
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:05,418
Things are starting to take shape.

76
00:03:05,419 --> 00:03:07,853
(With emotions growing complicated,
the random group date begins.)

77
00:03:08,855 --> 00:03:10,155
"Old and New."

78
00:03:10,156 --> 00:03:11,557
The two dates have different themes.

79
00:03:11,558 --> 00:03:12,391
(Who will end up with whom?)

80
00:03:12,392 --> 00:03:13,192
(Yeon House)

81
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:14,460
(Time to reveal the results of the draw)

82
00:03:14,461 --> 00:03:15,627
This is going to be fun.

83
00:03:16,163 --> 00:03:19,031
(The first one to reveal is Jung Won.)

84
00:03:19,533 --> 00:03:21,667
(Jin Young gets nervous
before Jung Won's reveal.)

85
00:03:21,668 --> 00:03:23,970
(And Ji Hye too.)

86
00:03:24,471 --> 00:03:26,338
Mine says "Old."

87
00:03:29,042 --> 00:03:29,875
Old.

88
00:03:29,876 --> 00:03:30,809
(Jung Won is in Old Group.)

89
00:03:31,044 --> 00:03:32,011
Old?

90
00:03:32,012 --> 00:03:33,946
I'm in New Group.

91
00:03:33,947 --> 00:03:35,981
- New.
- New.

92
00:03:35,982 --> 00:03:37,282
I see. New.

93
00:03:37,283 --> 00:03:38,684
The two of them are in different groups.

94
00:03:39,252 --> 00:03:40,252
I'm in Old Group.

95
00:03:41,888 --> 00:03:44,156
(Jung Won and Ji Hye are placed
in the same group.)

96
00:03:44,292 --> 00:03:45,524
I see. New.

97
00:03:46,827 --> 00:03:49,128
Jung Won and I ended up
in different groups.

98
00:03:49,196 --> 00:03:51,630
But Ji Hye drew the same team as Jung Won!

99
00:03:52,265 --> 00:03:55,467
It made me feel really anxious.

100
00:03:55,769 --> 00:03:57,069
Is that why you disappeared?

101
00:03:57,070 --> 00:03:57,837
Sorry.

102
00:03:57,838 --> 00:03:59,872
(Ji Hye gets a chance to go out
with Jung Won as she had hoped.)

103
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,440
Since we ended up on the same team,

104
00:04:02,042 --> 00:04:04,710
I hoped today would be...

105
00:04:05,078 --> 00:04:08,614
the day I could express my feelings...

106
00:04:08,615 --> 00:04:09,615
for him.

107
00:04:10,684 --> 00:04:11,516
(Next up is Si Won.)

108
00:04:11,517 --> 00:04:12,685
Please, deities of entertainment.

109
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,819
(Yu Jin and Ji Seung are curious.)

110
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:15,087
Please make it spicier.

111
00:04:15,722 --> 00:04:16,789
I drew New too.

112
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:17,589
New.

113
00:04:17,590 --> 00:04:18,791
(Si Won got New.)

114
00:04:18,792 --> 00:04:19,659
(Grinning)

115
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:20,993
Did Yu Jin draw the same one?

116
00:04:21,128 --> 00:04:21,861
She's smiling.

117
00:04:22,662 --> 00:04:24,563
- Wait. What about Ji Seung?
- This is so interesting!

118
00:04:24,798 --> 00:04:25,731
I drew Old too.

119
00:04:25,732 --> 00:04:27,433
(Ji Seung is in Old Group.)

120
00:04:27,668 --> 00:04:29,869
(Si Won and Ji Seung are separated.)

121
00:04:30,037 --> 00:04:31,938
- New?
- Yu Jin got New!

122
00:04:32,239 --> 00:04:33,806
She looked like a hamster just now.

123
00:04:34,408 --> 00:04:38,111
(Yu Jin ends up going out with Si Won.)

124
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:41,313
- Of course, it bothered me.
- It really did.

125
00:04:42,382 --> 00:04:45,350
I was hoping
things wouldn't change between us...

126
00:04:45,351 --> 00:04:46,385
or that nothing would change.

127
00:04:46,586 --> 00:04:47,753
That's...

128
00:04:48,355 --> 00:04:49,642
what I believed before.

129
00:04:49,643 --> 00:04:50,690
(Ji Seung was sure about Si Won.)

130
00:04:50,791 --> 00:04:52,291
But I'm not sure anymore.

131
00:04:53,661 --> 00:04:54,727
What does Gen Z do on dates?

132
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:56,996
All I can think of is taking
instant photos.

133
00:04:57,297 --> 00:04:59,365
- What do I do on a date?
- You're the youngest.

134
00:04:59,366 --> 00:05:00,799
- You're the youngest.
- Right.

135
00:05:01,369 --> 00:05:03,002
I was very satisfied.

136
00:05:04,004 --> 00:05:08,841
I felt relieved because I'd been...

137
00:05:08,842 --> 00:05:10,376
into Si Won.

138
00:05:11,745 --> 00:05:12,511
I'm in Old Group.

139
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:14,180
Hold on.

140
00:05:14,614 --> 00:05:17,115
(Now it's time
to reveal Ju Hee's results.)

141
00:05:17,116 --> 00:05:18,717
- Please let her be in Old Group.
- Old!

142
00:05:18,718 --> 00:05:19,685
(He hopes they'll be together.)

143
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,654
- Mine is Old.
- Old!

144
00:05:21,655 --> 00:05:22,888
(Ju Hee is in Old Group.)

145
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,457
I'm so glad.

146
00:05:24,458 --> 00:05:25,891
(Ju Hee and Yun So are placed
in the same group.)

147
00:05:25,892 --> 00:05:26,792
I'm Old too.

148
00:05:27,494 --> 00:05:28,994
See? All of them.

149
00:05:31,398 --> 00:05:32,331
I'm New.

150
00:05:32,966 --> 00:05:34,633
- Jin Woo?
- Jin Woo and Jin Young!

151
00:05:34,634 --> 00:05:35,935
(Jin Woo is in New Group.)

152
00:05:36,069 --> 00:05:38,303
This is insane.

153
00:05:38,304 --> 00:05:39,505
What will happen today?

154
00:05:40,173 --> 00:05:42,074
This is a huge variable.

155
00:05:43,643 --> 00:05:45,010
How could this happen?

156
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:50,916
"Arcade."

157
00:05:50,917 --> 00:05:54,353
(New Group's date will be at an arcade.)

158
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:56,188
- We're going to an arcade?
- We're going to an amusement park.

159
00:05:56,389 --> 00:05:57,103
Yes!

160
00:05:57,104 --> 00:05:58,523
(Old Group's date will be
at an amusement park.)

161
00:05:58,792 --> 00:06:02,094
(What will happen on their group dates?)

162
00:06:02,696 --> 00:06:04,930
Will we wear those headbands
at the theme park?

163
00:06:05,098 --> 00:06:06,965
- I think so.
- Yes.

164
00:06:07,802 --> 00:06:08,668
Today is going to be fun.

165
00:06:08,902 --> 00:06:09,735
I agree.

166
00:06:11,105 --> 00:06:12,204
Can we have some churros too?

167
00:06:12,906 --> 00:06:14,440
With vanilla ice cream? Yes.

168
00:06:14,841 --> 00:06:16,342
Sir Jung Won said
he'd buy them for everyone.

169
00:06:16,343 --> 00:06:18,177
So Ji Seung calls anyone
who buys her things "sir."

170
00:06:18,178 --> 00:06:20,779
Don't call each other that. That's weird.

171
00:06:21,982 --> 00:06:23,349
Let's all just be friends.

172
00:06:23,717 --> 00:06:24,283
Yes.

173
00:06:24,284 --> 00:06:25,418
We're practically the same age.

174
00:06:25,419 --> 00:06:26,285
Thirty-three isn't that old.

175
00:06:26,286 --> 00:06:28,854
Yun So, you're really young,
so use honorifics with everyone.

176
00:06:28,855 --> 00:06:30,256
(Reading the room)

177
00:06:30,757 --> 00:06:32,791
(Sulking)

178
00:06:32,792 --> 00:06:34,126
I'm not going to talk to her.

179
00:06:35,295 --> 00:06:37,429
Ju Hee is starting to smile
at Yun So's jokes now.

180
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:38,030
(Finding him cute)

181
00:06:38,564 --> 00:06:39,665
Have you all made your final picks?

182
00:06:39,833 --> 00:06:40,533
Sorry?

183
00:06:41,501 --> 00:06:42,333
What about it?

184
00:06:42,502 --> 00:06:45,037
There's no such thing
as a definite decision.

185
00:06:45,338 --> 00:06:46,471
- Really?
- Yes.

186
00:06:46,673 --> 00:06:48,140
But I've already made my final decision.

187
00:06:48,141 --> 00:06:48,907
Already?

188
00:06:48,908 --> 00:06:49,608
- Yes.
- That's fast.

189
00:06:50,644 --> 00:06:51,344
I'm curious.

190
00:06:52,045 --> 00:06:52,845
You are, aren't you?

191
00:06:54,247 --> 00:06:56,281
Yesterday's date...

192
00:06:56,683 --> 00:06:59,751
with Ji Hye was great.

193
00:07:00,053 --> 00:07:02,988
I wanted to show her my charms
without Jung Won around.

194
00:07:04,124 --> 00:07:06,091
So being grouped with Jung Won...

195
00:07:06,326 --> 00:07:07,326
made me feel a little uneasy.

196
00:07:07,594 --> 00:07:09,094
Oh, no.

197
00:07:09,696 --> 00:07:11,030
(He is bothered by Jung Won.)

198
00:07:11,031 --> 00:07:13,832
So all the men are bothered by Jung Won.

199
00:07:14,234 --> 00:07:15,301
There it is!

200
00:07:15,302 --> 00:07:16,101
- Really?
- No way!

201
00:07:16,102 --> 00:07:17,035
(They arrive at the theme park.)

202
00:07:17,036 --> 00:07:18,237
Hey, look. There's a dragon.

203
00:07:18,238 --> 00:07:19,104
It's pretty nice.

204
00:07:19,306 --> 00:07:20,539
(An amusement park perfect
for a retro date)

205
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:22,141
- It's so retro!
- This is going to be so fun!

206
00:07:22,676 --> 00:07:24,644
It's been a long time
since I last visited a theme park.

207
00:07:24,645 --> 00:07:26,445
Wait. That's a merry-go-round.

208
00:07:27,747 --> 00:07:29,049
- Are you okay with riding rides?
- Yes.

209
00:07:29,050 --> 00:07:29,848
Take it together!

210
00:07:30,957 --> 00:07:32,958
Yun So is cute! "Take it together!"

211
00:07:33,088 --> 00:07:33,753
So cute.

212
00:07:33,754 --> 00:07:34,754
(Satisfied)

213
00:07:34,755 --> 00:07:35,922
Wait. That's...

214
00:07:37,857 --> 00:07:38,591
"Fairy Tale Castle."

215
00:07:38,792 --> 00:07:40,092
- What's that?
- I don't know.

216
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,228
(Touching him)

217
00:07:42,696 --> 00:07:44,065
(They burst into laughter
at small things.)

218
00:07:44,066 --> 00:07:45,164
- What's that?
- It's a Fairy Tale Castle.

219
00:07:45,498 --> 00:07:46,398
No way. Really?

220
00:07:46,967 --> 00:07:48,533
(Turning around)

221
00:07:48,534 --> 00:07:50,036
Let's take pictures over there later.

222
00:07:50,837 --> 00:07:51,870
At the Fairy Tale Castle?

223
00:07:52,339 --> 00:07:54,473
Hold on.
Things aren't looking good for Jun Han.

224
00:07:54,607 --> 00:07:57,943
Jun Han seems to have lost confidence.

225
00:07:58,612 --> 00:07:59,779
Let's ride the bumper cars.

226
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:01,147
- Bumper cars sound nice.
- Bumper cars?

227
00:08:01,148 --> 00:08:02,715
Let's start with the wildest one.

228
00:08:06,628 --> 00:08:08,662
- Is it a two-person ride?
- It's a two-person ride!

229
00:08:08,822 --> 00:08:09,989
(If that's the case...)

230
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:12,051
Ju Hee, come on. You can drive.

231
00:08:12,052 --> 00:08:12,992
(He calls Ju Hee right away.)

232
00:08:12,993 --> 00:08:15,561
Ju Hee, come on. You can drive.

233
00:08:15,562 --> 00:08:16,529
- Me?
- Yes.

234
00:08:16,763 --> 00:08:17,596
You drive.

235
00:08:17,864 --> 00:08:19,498
- Really? Can I?
- You drive.

236
00:08:19,499 --> 00:08:21,767
- That feels a little off.
- You can drive this one, can't you?

237
00:08:21,768 --> 00:08:22,868
That would make me look really bad.

238
00:08:25,005 --> 00:08:27,173
He's been giving
off younger-boyfriend vibes for a while.

239
00:08:27,274 --> 00:08:29,442
He seems comfortable around her
since their ages were revealed.

240
00:08:29,809 --> 00:08:31,877
"Ju Hee! You drive."

241
00:08:31,878 --> 00:08:32,744
"Ju Hee!"

242
00:08:32,745 --> 00:08:33,645
"Ju Hee, over here!"

243
00:08:33,646 --> 00:08:34,746
(Copying Yun So)

244
00:08:34,747 --> 00:08:35,881
(Reading the room)

245
00:08:35,882 --> 00:08:37,115
So it's a two-person ride?

246
00:08:37,284 --> 00:08:38,084
Seems so.

247
00:08:39,252 --> 00:08:40,019
(Spotting Ji Hye)

248
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:41,320
I'm a good driver!
Who wants to ride with me?

249
00:08:41,721 --> 00:08:42,954
Oh, no.

250
00:08:42,955 --> 00:08:45,793
- Isn't everyone getting one?
- Sorry?

251
00:08:45,794 --> 00:08:46,658
(Ji Hye didn't hear him.)

252
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,827
The two of you will ride one, right?

253
00:08:48,828 --> 00:08:49,761
The two...

254
00:08:51,231 --> 00:08:55,768
(He calls her over again.)

255
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:58,304
Oh, no.

256
00:08:58,305 --> 00:08:59,338
(His signal doesn't reach her.)

257
00:08:59,339 --> 00:09:00,639
Oh, no.

258
00:09:01,574 --> 00:09:02,808
(Jun Han ends up with Ji Seung.)

259
00:09:02,809 --> 00:09:04,643
- I mean, you...
- Yes?

260
00:09:04,844 --> 00:09:05,677
You're so big.

261
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:07,980
Isn't it one car per person?

262
00:09:07,981 --> 00:09:08,748
It's a two-person ride.

263
00:09:08,749 --> 00:09:10,148
- Do you want to drive? Or should I?
- I see.

264
00:09:10,149 --> 00:09:11,850
You drive.

265
00:09:11,851 --> 00:09:12,818
No, you do it.

266
00:09:12,819 --> 00:09:13,853
You drive.

267
00:09:13,854 --> 00:09:14,820
No, you can do it.

268
00:09:14,821 --> 00:09:15,520
No.

269
00:09:15,521 --> 00:09:16,488
You want me to?

270
00:09:16,489 --> 00:09:17,656
(She goes to Jung Won with a big smile.)

271
00:09:17,959 --> 00:09:19,091
- You trust me, right?
- Yes.

272
00:09:19,092 --> 00:09:20,125
Let's go.

273
00:09:20,827 --> 00:09:21,560
Taking one by yourself?

274
00:09:22,329 --> 00:09:23,195
No, let's take it together.

275
00:09:24,164 --> 00:09:25,364
Are you looking in the mirror?

276
00:09:25,665 --> 00:09:26,398
I don't know.

277
00:09:28,802 --> 00:09:30,469
Oh, no.

278
00:09:30,838 --> 00:09:32,905
I hope it won't be all white and blurry.

279
00:09:32,906 --> 00:09:33,939
- No way.
- Right?

280
00:09:35,542 --> 00:09:36,849
- They look good together.
- They really do.

281
00:09:37,978 --> 00:09:40,713
(Ju Hee and Yun So look
so close in the picture.)

282
00:09:41,581 --> 00:09:42,481
That scared me.

283
00:09:42,482 --> 00:09:44,316
(An alarm goes off
to signal the start of the ride.)

284
00:09:44,317 --> 00:09:45,284
There we go.

285
00:09:46,586 --> 00:09:48,587
How do I drive this thing?
Why isn't it moving?

286
00:09:52,859 --> 00:09:54,893
This is pretty rough.

287
00:09:55,562 --> 00:09:56,829
It's rough.

288
00:09:57,063 --> 00:09:58,230
It's rougher than I expected.

289
00:09:58,231 --> 00:09:59,031
(Excited)

290
00:10:00,373 --> 00:10:01,133
Let's run away!

291
00:10:01,134 --> 00:10:03,034
- Get away from them!
- I'm sorry.

292
00:10:03,544 --> 00:10:04,217
Run away!

293
00:10:04,664 --> 00:10:07,230
I'll hold your bag in place.

294
00:10:07,231 --> 00:10:09,364
(Using her bag as an excuse)

295
00:10:12,431 --> 00:10:13,497
I'll hold your bag in place.

296
00:10:14,964 --> 00:10:15,764
Just leave it.

297
00:10:16,664 --> 00:10:19,697
(Her firm answer makes
his hand hover in the air.)

298
00:10:20,397 --> 00:10:22,196
You get the biggest hit
when you go head-on.

299
00:10:22,197 --> 00:10:24,731
Let me go all the way there.

300
00:10:26,297 --> 00:10:30,496
(The two can't stop laughing.)

301
00:10:30,497 --> 00:10:31,530
Wait. Where are you going?

302
00:10:31,531 --> 00:10:33,064
We get back in.

303
00:10:33,397 --> 00:10:34,264
Wait!

304
00:10:36,064 --> 00:10:37,497
- Are you okay?
- Are you all right?

305
00:10:37,997 --> 00:10:39,330
(The fun bumper car time ends.)

306
00:10:39,331 --> 00:10:42,563
- That was fun.
- That was really fun.

307
00:10:42,564 --> 00:10:43,596
(His hand is still hovering.)

308
00:10:43,597 --> 00:10:44,497
That was fun.

309
00:10:46,464 --> 00:10:48,864
- I had fun.
- It was fun.

310
00:10:49,331 --> 00:10:50,930
Shall we get coffee?

311
00:10:50,931 --> 00:10:52,131
Yes. Let's get coffee.

312
00:10:56,064 --> 00:10:57,497
- That was fun.
- Coffee?

313
00:11:01,031 --> 00:11:03,430
She just looks at him, and he comes.

314
00:11:03,431 --> 00:11:05,264
(Feeling her gaze,
Jung Won walks over to her side.)

315
00:11:09,364 --> 00:11:11,163
I want to wear a headband too.

316
00:11:11,164 --> 00:11:12,863
- We could buy one there.
- Are there some over there?

317
00:11:12,864 --> 00:11:14,431
- I see some there.
- You do? Do they sell them?

318
00:11:14,864 --> 00:11:18,830
(He doesn't seem to blend in.)

319
00:11:18,831 --> 00:11:20,697
He must be so annoyed.

320
00:11:21,264 --> 00:11:23,297
He can only watch her from behind...

321
00:11:24,131 --> 00:11:25,156
unless he walks in front of her.

322
00:11:25,157 --> 00:11:27,196
He tries to join them,

323
00:11:27,197 --> 00:11:28,996
- but he can't.
- How can he?

324
00:11:28,997 --> 00:11:30,197
It's impossible.

325
00:11:31,297 --> 00:11:32,277
(The second ride is the Viking.)

326
00:11:32,278 --> 00:11:34,297
Let me check your tickets.

327
00:11:35,331 --> 00:11:38,797
(Ji Hye sits next to Jung Won again.)

328
00:11:42,931 --> 00:11:44,563
Oh, dear.

329
00:11:44,564 --> 00:11:46,564
(Jun Han is late again.)

330
00:11:47,731 --> 00:11:48,897
Let's sit here.

331
00:11:50,831 --> 00:11:52,163
(Jun Han sits with Ji Seung
in front of Ji Hye.)

332
00:11:52,164 --> 00:11:55,464
Why is there a safety belt here?

333
00:11:56,331 --> 00:11:57,963
- Are you scared?
- I am.

334
00:11:57,964 --> 00:12:00,130
(He tries to hide it, but he feels sad.)

335
00:12:00,131 --> 00:12:02,031
I feel bad.

336
00:12:03,297 --> 00:12:07,696
- Ji Hye is acting like he's not there.
- Right, on purpose.

337
00:12:07,697 --> 00:12:09,930
- On purpose.
- It's like she's ignoring him.

338
00:12:09,931 --> 00:12:12,331
She's making it clear...

339
00:12:12,631 --> 00:12:16,264
that she's not into him anymore.

340
00:12:16,697 --> 00:12:17,964
Poor Jun Han.

341
00:12:19,564 --> 00:12:21,864
(Yun So and Ju Hee are sitting
across from them.)

342
00:12:22,464 --> 00:12:23,963
- It's so hot.
- I know!

343
00:12:23,964 --> 00:12:26,197
- It's really hot.
- I feel like we're going to get tanned.

344
00:12:27,764 --> 00:12:29,797
Is it too hot?

345
00:12:30,397 --> 00:12:33,964
(Yun So shades her face with his hand.)

346
00:12:34,797 --> 00:12:37,031
(Smiling)

347
00:12:38,531 --> 00:12:39,397
It's moving.

348
00:12:40,597 --> 00:12:42,097
It goes high.

349
00:12:43,831 --> 00:12:44,697
Wait.

350
00:12:45,664 --> 00:12:46,497
It's so intense.

351
00:12:47,264 --> 00:12:49,131
(That's cute.)

352
00:12:49,497 --> 00:12:54,031
(The pirate ship goes up
to almost a 90-degree angle.)

353
00:12:56,664 --> 00:12:57,697
Please!

354
00:12:58,164 --> 00:12:58,996
Wait.

355
00:12:58,997 --> 00:13:00,830
Ji Hye, seriously.

356
00:13:00,831 --> 00:13:01,831
Relax.

357
00:13:02,564 --> 00:13:03,488
(They get close while scared.)

358
00:13:03,489 --> 00:13:05,463
She held his hand briefly.

359
00:13:05,464 --> 00:13:07,031
It's making my hands sweatier.

360
00:13:07,964 --> 00:13:09,331
(Pale)

361
00:13:09,564 --> 00:13:10,397
It's refreshing.

362
00:13:10,664 --> 00:13:14,497
(He's also anxious.)

363
00:13:15,131 --> 00:13:17,764
It goes higher than I thought.

364
00:13:19,397 --> 00:13:21,797
(Heart, calm down.)

365
00:13:22,597 --> 00:13:23,931
(Embarrassed)

366
00:13:25,897 --> 00:13:31,697
(Yun So is terrified,
and Ju Hee finds it funny.)

367
00:13:32,697 --> 00:13:35,396
(His face freezes up from nervousness.)

368
00:13:35,397 --> 00:13:36,297
This is so funny.

369
00:13:37,231 --> 00:13:38,464
Look at his face.

370
00:13:38,931 --> 00:13:40,296
(Look at Yun So's face.)

371
00:13:40,297 --> 00:13:41,731
His face looks pale.

372
00:13:42,631 --> 00:13:46,031
(Pale)

373
00:13:46,664 --> 00:13:50,297
(The terrifying pirate ship ride ends.)

374
00:13:50,664 --> 00:13:52,196
- This is it.
- We're here.

375
00:13:52,197 --> 00:13:53,364
It's nice.

376
00:13:54,164 --> 00:13:56,097
This place? It's cool.

377
00:13:56,864 --> 00:13:58,630
I haven't been to this kind of arcade
in a while.

378
00:13:58,631 --> 00:14:00,397
- It's so pretty.
- That looks fun.

379
00:14:01,031 --> 00:14:01,964
Shall we play the claw machine?

380
00:14:02,331 --> 00:14:03,864
They seem to be in a good mood.

381
00:14:04,097 --> 00:14:05,663
Let's win some plushies.

382
00:14:05,664 --> 00:14:06,631
Let's see what they have.

383
00:14:07,231 --> 00:14:08,463
Do you have a favorite character?

384
00:14:08,464 --> 00:14:09,397
Loopy.

385
00:14:09,664 --> 00:14:10,496
Do you like Loopy?

386
00:14:10,497 --> 00:14:12,096
Can you get that? It's too big.

387
00:14:12,097 --> 00:14:12,930
Loopy?

388
00:14:12,931 --> 00:14:13,731
Should I get it for you?

389
00:14:13,864 --> 00:14:14,830
- Really?
- Do you want one?

390
00:14:14,831 --> 00:14:15,697
Try it.

391
00:14:16,397 --> 00:14:17,231
Hold on.

392
00:14:17,731 --> 00:14:18,696
Is that good?

393
00:14:18,697 --> 00:14:20,497
- No?
- A little higher.

394
00:14:20,897 --> 00:14:21,697
- Is it good now?
- Okay.

395
00:14:25,764 --> 00:14:27,531
(That was close.)

396
00:14:27,731 --> 00:14:29,064
You were so close.

397
00:14:30,331 --> 00:14:31,863
Do you really want one?

398
00:14:31,864 --> 00:14:32,797
- Loopy?
- Yes.

399
00:14:33,731 --> 00:14:35,097
Well, it does look cute.

400
00:14:35,697 --> 00:14:37,364
If it looks cute, I should get it.

401
00:14:38,131 --> 00:14:39,796
Should we try it one last time?

402
00:14:39,797 --> 00:14:42,430
When we leave Yeon House, you can eat
at my restaurant for free forever.

403
00:14:42,431 --> 00:14:44,863
- Forever.
- As long as you're happy, I'm happy.

404
00:14:44,864 --> 00:14:46,497
If this can make you happy,
that's enough for me.

405
00:14:47,231 --> 00:14:48,830
She's an angel.

406
00:14:48,831 --> 00:14:49,764
- I know.
- Let's go.

407
00:14:51,797 --> 00:14:54,396
(Jin Woo was having a hard time
after being rejected by Ji Hye.)

408
00:14:54,397 --> 00:14:58,130
Try to have a good time on the date...

409
00:14:58,131 --> 00:15:00,830
for your date's sake too.

410
00:15:00,831 --> 00:15:04,164
It'd be better to have
this kind of mindset.

411
00:15:04,189 --> 00:15:05,356
I might ask you out.

412
00:15:07,131 --> 00:15:09,296
(And Jin Woo showed some interest
in Jin Young.)

413
00:15:09,297 --> 00:15:10,330
- Me?
- Yes.

414
00:15:10,331 --> 00:15:11,097
Okay.

415
00:15:12,064 --> 00:15:13,497
Just like I practiced.

416
00:15:13,964 --> 00:15:15,463
I should drag it from the end.

417
00:15:15,464 --> 00:15:16,464
You've practiced enough.

418
00:15:16,997 --> 00:15:18,297
Win one for him.

419
00:15:19,731 --> 00:15:22,496
No way!

420
00:15:22,497 --> 00:15:24,364
- What?
- What?

421
00:15:27,397 --> 00:15:28,730
What?

422
00:15:28,731 --> 00:15:29,696
(Surprised)

423
00:15:29,697 --> 00:15:30,496
Did you see that?

424
00:15:30,497 --> 00:15:32,596
- What? I'm stunned.
- Did you see that?

425
00:15:32,597 --> 00:15:34,131
Did you see that?

426
00:15:34,997 --> 00:15:36,364
She pulled that off?

427
00:15:36,831 --> 00:15:37,863
Jin Young is great.

428
00:15:37,864 --> 00:15:39,264
That's impressive.

429
00:15:39,564 --> 00:15:41,463
Since they moved into Yeon House,

430
00:15:41,464 --> 00:15:44,930
- Jin Young is the first person...
- She's the first.

431
00:15:44,931 --> 00:15:46,797
- who has done something so kind for him.
- You're right.

432
00:15:47,064 --> 00:15:49,663
Jin Woo won't be able
to get her out of his mind.

433
00:15:49,664 --> 00:15:50,897
(Will this make Jin Woo fall for her?)

434
00:15:52,797 --> 00:15:54,331
- What?
- This is me.

435
00:15:54,797 --> 00:15:55,664
I did this.

436
00:15:56,331 --> 00:15:57,196
It's me.

437
00:15:57,197 --> 00:15:58,831
I told you I'd win this for you.

438
00:15:59,664 --> 00:16:00,697
He's so excited.

439
00:16:01,164 --> 00:16:02,963
- Are you happy?
- This is awesome.

440
00:16:02,964 --> 00:16:05,196
Go to sleep holding this.

441
00:16:05,197 --> 00:16:06,664
- Carry this around with you today.
- Okay.

442
00:16:07,831 --> 00:16:09,296
I think we look alike.

443
00:16:09,297 --> 00:16:10,363
She looks just like you.

444
00:16:10,364 --> 00:16:11,163
Give me a wink.

445
00:16:11,164 --> 00:16:12,197
(Winking)

446
00:16:12,697 --> 00:16:14,397
That was cute.

447
00:16:16,397 --> 00:16:17,296
I really appreciated it.

448
00:16:17,297 --> 00:16:18,997
I even have a Loopy phone case.

449
00:16:19,497 --> 00:16:20,497
I really love Loopy.

450
00:16:21,031 --> 00:16:23,897
I was really grateful,
and I thought she was a good person.

451
00:16:25,031 --> 00:16:26,464
Hey, let me take a look.

452
00:16:27,131 --> 00:16:27,997
Should I carry you?

453
00:16:28,397 --> 00:16:31,263
- You shouldn't touch the ground.
- Carry me around on your back.

454
00:16:31,264 --> 00:16:32,297
Okay. I'll show you.

455
00:16:32,997 --> 00:16:34,463
Yu Jin seems jealous,

456
00:16:34,464 --> 00:16:36,296
so Si Won wants to try too.

457
00:16:36,297 --> 00:16:37,363
It bruised his ego a little.

458
00:16:37,364 --> 00:16:38,896
Let's lift that one.

459
00:16:38,897 --> 00:16:40,363
This one? Can it be lifted?

460
00:16:40,364 --> 00:16:43,664
Let's drag it and put it
in the corner like this.

461
00:16:43,864 --> 00:16:45,597
It's not as easy as it seems.

462
00:16:46,197 --> 00:16:48,297
It's not that easy.

463
00:16:48,864 --> 00:16:50,064
Let me try this.

464
00:16:50,931 --> 00:16:52,330
Please, Si Won.

465
00:16:52,331 --> 00:16:53,397
(Lifting)

466
00:16:55,331 --> 00:16:58,796
My goodness!

467
00:16:58,797 --> 00:16:59,930
- He did it.
- My gosh.

468
00:16:59,931 --> 00:17:01,096
(Jackpot!)

469
00:17:01,097 --> 00:17:02,130
It slid.

470
00:17:02,131 --> 00:17:04,731
- Where is that arcade?
- It slid in.

471
00:17:06,964 --> 00:17:07,930
Amazing!

472
00:17:07,931 --> 00:17:09,530
I've never won anything
from a claw machine before.

473
00:17:09,531 --> 00:17:10,496
Let's win them all.

474
00:17:10,497 --> 00:17:14,263
- That's awesome.
- Can I try?

475
00:17:14,264 --> 00:17:15,596
- Hey, Loopy.
- Loopy.

476
00:17:15,597 --> 00:17:18,064
- Win something for me.
- My gosh.

477
00:17:18,397 --> 00:17:19,230
This is fun.

478
00:17:19,231 --> 00:17:21,463
- That was fun.
- How did we improve so quickly?

479
00:17:21,464 --> 00:17:22,897
I know! We got better.

480
00:17:23,231 --> 00:17:25,463
- I'm sweating so much.
- Me too.

481
00:17:25,464 --> 00:17:26,996
- Were you nervous?
- I got too excited.

482
00:17:26,997 --> 00:17:29,096
This is the most fun I've had
since I came to Yeon House.

483
00:17:29,097 --> 00:17:30,231
Let's go.

484
00:17:30,797 --> 00:17:34,764
(Team Old moves on to the next spot.)

485
00:17:35,264 --> 00:17:36,697
Is this a photo studio?

486
00:17:37,197 --> 00:17:38,664
We're going to take a family photo.

487
00:17:39,764 --> 00:17:42,764
Since they're the old team,
they'll take an old family photo.

488
00:17:44,331 --> 00:17:45,330
Oh, dear.

489
00:17:45,331 --> 00:17:46,364
Seriously.

490
00:17:47,031 --> 00:17:47,997
Amazing vibes here.

491
00:17:48,497 --> 00:17:51,130
(Full of retro items)

492
00:17:51,131 --> 00:17:52,263
That's fun.

493
00:17:52,264 --> 00:17:53,397
(A 40-year-old photo studio)

494
00:17:53,797 --> 00:17:55,463
Get a little closer.

495
00:17:55,464 --> 00:17:56,964
Like a family photo from back then.

496
00:17:57,497 --> 00:17:59,164
Okay, that's good.

497
00:17:59,731 --> 00:18:01,064
I like that.

498
00:18:03,764 --> 00:18:04,997
Why is Yun So so stiff?

499
00:18:05,464 --> 00:18:06,797
In 1, 2.

500
00:18:12,797 --> 00:18:13,763
That's cute.

501
00:18:13,764 --> 00:18:15,331
(A vintage-style family photo,
perfect for Team Old)

502
00:18:15,564 --> 00:18:18,197
Do you want to take more pictures?

503
00:18:19,315 --> 00:18:21,196
As you've been getting to know each other,

504
00:18:21,197 --> 00:18:22,930
has there been anyone
you've called dibs on?

505
00:18:22,931 --> 00:18:24,997
- Call dibs on?
- "You're mine?"

506
00:18:26,297 --> 00:18:27,697
Pictures in pairs?

507
00:18:28,531 --> 00:18:29,730
- Do you want one?
- Let's do it.

508
00:18:29,731 --> 00:18:30,864
Let's take pictures in pairs.

509
00:18:31,397 --> 00:18:33,264
(Jun Han misses Ji Hye again.)

510
00:18:33,664 --> 00:18:34,531
Let's take one.

511
00:18:34,897 --> 00:18:36,930
(Yun So will take one with Ju Hee.)

512
00:18:36,931 --> 00:18:38,864
- Let's take one.
- Okay.

513
00:18:39,397 --> 00:18:40,663
Who wants to go first?

514
00:18:40,664 --> 00:18:42,597
- Let's take one quickly.
- Okay.

515
00:18:42,831 --> 00:18:44,764
Can we switch seats?
The right is my good side.

516
00:18:46,231 --> 00:18:47,597
So you're a couple?

517
00:18:47,897 --> 00:18:48,831
He's doing a good job.

518
00:18:49,064 --> 00:18:49,996
Well...

519
00:18:49,997 --> 00:18:50,830
- We don't know.
- No.

520
00:18:50,831 --> 00:18:51,631
We're not sure.

521
00:18:54,597 --> 00:18:56,797
(Sad)

522
00:18:57,031 --> 00:18:59,564
How do people usually pose?

523
00:18:59,897 --> 00:19:03,264
Your expression looks so awkward now.

524
00:19:03,497 --> 00:19:06,863
It's like you're saying,
"We're strangers."

525
00:19:06,864 --> 00:19:07,730
Not her shoulder.

526
00:19:07,731 --> 00:19:08,931
- Not the shoulder?
- Put it down.

527
00:19:09,397 --> 00:19:10,364
Her waist.

528
00:19:12,964 --> 00:19:14,696
Why are you so shy?

529
00:19:14,697 --> 00:19:16,630
- Can we do whatever we want?
- Yes.

530
00:19:16,631 --> 00:19:17,831
- I like that.
- Relax your hands.

531
00:19:19,031 --> 00:19:20,231
- Let's cross our legs.
- Okay.

532
00:19:21,864 --> 00:19:23,397
I feel bad.

533
00:19:28,264 --> 00:19:29,897
Aren't we almost like a married couple?

534
00:19:32,131 --> 00:19:34,130
I'm the most myself...

535
00:19:34,131 --> 00:19:36,831
when I'm with Jung Won.

536
00:19:37,464 --> 00:19:42,697
He just makes me laugh nonstop
without even realizing it.

537
00:19:43,364 --> 00:19:46,531
I had a wonderful time.

538
00:19:47,431 --> 00:19:49,097
I just liked everything.

539
00:19:50,564 --> 00:19:53,031
Actually, that's the best it can get.

540
00:19:53,864 --> 00:19:56,030
He brings out the real you?

541
00:19:56,031 --> 00:19:57,197
Nothing beats that.

542
00:20:03,936 --> 00:20:05,603
They really looked great together.

543
00:20:06,305 --> 00:20:09,440
It felt like Ji Hye's feelings were
shifting more toward Jung Won,

544
00:20:10,476 --> 00:20:12,911
and that really made me unsettled.

545
00:20:14,906 --> 00:20:17,508
Jun Han's a completely different person
from Day Two.

546
00:20:18,718 --> 00:20:19,651
Oh my, look at the two of you!

547
00:20:19,652 --> 00:20:21,052
(The two are becoming
more natural together.)

548
00:20:21,053 --> 00:20:21,787
Sorry?

549
00:20:22,488 --> 00:20:24,722
I really enjoyed taking pictures with her.

550
00:20:25,557 --> 00:20:28,693
When we saw the photos afterward,
they were actually hilarious.

551
00:20:28,694 --> 00:20:30,328
We both looked so funny,

552
00:20:30,529 --> 00:20:31,797
- but even then,
- They look great together.

553
00:20:31,798 --> 00:20:33,231
they really felt like couple photos.

554
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:35,034
We looked so good together.

555
00:20:36,702 --> 00:20:39,304
(Next up are Yun So and Ju Hee.)

556
00:20:39,639 --> 00:20:40,405
Can I do a peace sign?

557
00:20:42,041 --> 00:20:43,575
Our hands feel a little awkward,
don't they?

558
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:45,343
You're keeping your hands
a little too neatly.

559
00:20:46,212 --> 00:20:49,047
Rest your arm on his knee.

560
00:20:49,048 --> 00:20:50,115
(Me?)

561
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:52,350
Are you two not close?

562
00:20:52,551 --> 00:20:53,551
Us?

563
00:20:53,886 --> 00:20:55,053
Put your hand on his knee.

564
00:20:55,054 --> 00:20:57,589
(The photographer's suggestion brings
the two even closer.)

565
00:20:57,874 --> 00:21:00,742
When she rested her arm on my knee,
my heart skipped a beat.

566
00:21:02,261 --> 00:21:05,129
We already had a little physical contact
on the bumper cars,

567
00:21:05,898 --> 00:21:06,831
so I was excited then too.

568
00:21:06,899 --> 00:21:10,868
Getting close again at the studio
made me feel really happy.

569
00:21:11,871 --> 00:21:13,672
(Even the smallest touch
makes Yun So's heart race.)

570
00:21:13,673 --> 00:21:14,473
Smile.

571
00:21:17,309 --> 00:21:18,609
We were much closer than usual,

572
00:21:18,811 --> 00:21:22,680
and I really enjoyed the time with Yun So.

573
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:24,149
"Really."

574
00:21:24,383 --> 00:21:27,385
(How did Yun So and Ju Hee's
heart-fluttering photos turn out?)

575
00:21:29,055 --> 00:21:30,722
- Oh, that photo looks really good.
- It's nice.

576
00:21:31,957 --> 00:21:32,924
How lovely!

577
00:21:32,925 --> 00:21:34,759
(And Jun Han and Ji Seung's photos
with a newlywed vibe)

578
00:21:35,594 --> 00:21:37,328
- Let's go.
- That's so hilarious.

579
00:21:37,863 --> 00:21:39,263
I'm having so much fun today.

580
00:21:40,232 --> 00:21:41,098
The second floor here.

581
00:21:41,099 --> 00:21:42,667
(Meanwhile, where is
Team New's second stop?)

582
00:21:42,668 --> 00:21:45,503
This kind of looks
like a self-photo studio.

583
00:21:47,139 --> 00:21:52,143
(A self-photo studio
where you take your own pictures)

584
00:21:52,445 --> 00:21:54,646
Let's go in and figure out
what poses to do. We have 15 minutes.

585
00:21:54,647 --> 00:21:56,314
Sure. Should we just start
taking pictures?

586
00:21:56,482 --> 00:21:57,615
Let's just take them naturally.

587
00:21:57,983 --> 00:21:59,417
I'll sit over here.

588
00:21:59,418 --> 00:22:01,919
(Yu Jin and Si Won start
their photo shoot.)

589
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:03,654
How should we pose
to make the pictures look good?

590
00:22:04,423 --> 00:22:05,289
How should we pose?

591
00:22:05,290 --> 00:22:07,125
(Gently laying her hand)

592
00:22:09,595 --> 00:22:12,030
(Stiff)

593
00:22:12,164 --> 00:22:13,098
This feels a little awkward.

594
00:22:13,099 --> 00:22:15,133
- It does.
- What should we do?

595
00:22:16,435 --> 00:22:17,168
Tell me.

596
00:22:17,169 --> 00:22:19,705
(Their first couple photo shoot starts
off a little awkwardly.)

597
00:22:19,706 --> 00:22:23,007
Then I'll just lean on you instead.

598
00:22:23,275 --> 00:22:26,010
Hold the clicker lower
so the cord doesn't show.

599
00:22:26,011 --> 00:22:26,811
Like this?

600
00:22:26,912 --> 00:22:29,514
Or you could hold it with your other hand.

601
00:22:29,582 --> 00:22:32,483
- So the cord doesn't show?
- Yes, try to hide it.

602
00:22:32,752 --> 00:22:33,886
In 1, 2, 3.

603
00:22:34,389 --> 00:22:35,353
Those two look so good together.

604
00:22:36,756 --> 00:22:39,024
- How is it?
- Should I lean a little closer to you?

605
00:22:39,025 --> 00:22:39,758
Like how?

606
00:22:40,426 --> 00:22:41,726
Your pose looks good.

607
00:22:41,727 --> 00:22:42,862
I should move a little closer to you.

608
00:22:42,863 --> 00:22:43,528
Sure.

609
00:22:43,863 --> 00:22:44,696
Good.

610
00:22:45,264 --> 00:22:46,065
That's nice.

611
00:22:46,932 --> 00:22:48,100
Good. Just keep it natural.

612
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:52,804
- This looks nice.
- Oh, I like this.

613
00:22:52,805 --> 00:22:54,840
How about we look at each other?

614
00:22:55,708 --> 00:22:56,675
I like that.

615
00:22:57,276 --> 00:22:58,142
You know...

616
00:22:58,511 --> 00:23:00,245
Let's just keep pressing the button
and take pictures.

617
00:23:00,846 --> 00:23:02,914
- I think that'll look much better.
- It does feel natural.

618
00:23:02,915 --> 00:23:04,450
Right? Just like this.

619
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:06,250
You're good at this.

620
00:23:06,752 --> 00:23:08,120
- Isn't it nice?
- You're good.

621
00:23:08,121 --> 00:23:08,986
Like this?

622
00:23:09,388 --> 00:23:10,688
I think we should keep doing it this way.

623
00:23:10,689 --> 00:23:11,556
Right.

624
00:23:12,424 --> 00:23:15,226
(They can't contain their smiles.)

625
00:23:15,227 --> 00:23:17,228
- Oh, gosh!
- Even I feel awkward!

626
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:19,798
- You know how it feels.
- Yes.

627
00:23:19,799 --> 00:23:20,999
(Shaking)

628
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,834
I might break this chair today.

629
00:23:25,004 --> 00:23:26,671
(Sliding on)

630
00:23:28,140 --> 00:23:30,875
Yu Jin is having a blast.

631
00:23:31,243 --> 00:23:32,644
I've never seen her this happy.

632
00:23:32,945 --> 00:23:33,912
Let's just keep taking pictures.

633
00:23:34,346 --> 00:23:35,713
Let's just take a whole bunch.

634
00:23:36,916 --> 00:23:38,083
These two have such great chemistry.

635
00:23:38,651 --> 00:23:39,484
(Glancing)

636
00:23:40,019 --> 00:23:41,152
(Shy)

637
00:23:42,754 --> 00:23:43,421
Like this.

638
00:23:44,090 --> 00:23:45,423
At this rate, they might end up kissing.

639
00:23:45,491 --> 00:23:47,158
I really enjoyed it.

640
00:23:47,627 --> 00:23:49,327
Nothing felt awkward with Si Won.

641
00:23:49,762 --> 00:23:51,930
The poses came naturally,

642
00:23:52,599 --> 00:23:55,500
every little interaction felt effortless,

643
00:23:56,335 --> 00:23:58,202
and I found him really cute.

644
00:23:58,437 --> 00:24:01,172
I think I liked him even more after that.

645
00:24:01,207 --> 00:24:02,908
At this point, they're basically dating.

646
00:24:04,543 --> 00:24:05,843
Let's take an extreme close-up.

647
00:24:07,658 --> 00:24:09,113
- This is making me a bit nervous though.
- Why?

648
00:24:09,114 --> 00:24:10,815
An extreme close-up with Si Won?

649
00:24:10,816 --> 00:24:11,983
Come on. It'll be fine.

650
00:24:13,519 --> 00:24:14,552
Should we make flower poses
with our hands around our faces?

651
00:24:14,987 --> 00:24:16,354
- Okay.
- Are you okay with that pose?

652
00:24:16,355 --> 00:24:17,922
I'm really trying
a lot of new things today.

653
00:24:19,191 --> 00:24:20,778
You do the flower pose,
and I'll just look at you.

654
00:24:20,779 --> 00:24:21,325
Okay.

655
00:24:21,493 --> 00:24:22,927
But then won't you be out of the frame?

656
00:24:22,928 --> 00:24:24,061
I'll stay close enough.

657
00:24:25,231 --> 00:24:28,133
He must really want
to keep looking at Yu Jin.

658
00:24:30,736 --> 00:24:31,436
How does it look?

659
00:24:32,171 --> 00:24:33,838
This one is cute too.
You think so?

660
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:34,973
I think you came out really well.

661
00:24:35,809 --> 00:24:37,108
Were you only looking at me?

662
00:24:38,944 --> 00:24:40,211
No. I looked at myself too.

663
00:24:40,913 --> 00:24:43,715
I think taking pictures with Yu Jin made
my heart flutter even more.

664
00:24:44,016 --> 00:24:46,284
It was exciting,

665
00:24:46,418 --> 00:24:47,885
It definitely was.

666
00:24:48,321 --> 00:24:52,857
and I really enjoyed doing
something together with her.

667
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:55,727
After that photo shoot,

668
00:24:55,728 --> 00:24:57,896
I think my feelings for her grew
even stronger.

669
00:25:04,336 --> 00:25:07,505
Once they finally had
some real physical contact,

670
00:25:07,573 --> 00:25:09,007
- they...
- They definitely seemed a lot closer.

671
00:25:09,008 --> 00:25:10,108
- Right.
- Hold on.

672
00:25:10,109 --> 00:25:12,410
Now, I'm curious
how Jin Young and Jin Woo did.

673
00:25:12,611 --> 00:25:14,345
Jin Woo, let's see what you've got!

674
00:25:15,314 --> 00:25:16,281
Go for it.

675
00:25:17,082 --> 00:25:19,149
Let's do the pose we talked about first.

676
00:25:19,150 --> 00:25:20,384
The pose we talked about?

677
00:25:20,786 --> 00:25:22,487
- Then I should just stay still, right?
- Yes.

678
00:25:23,689 --> 00:25:24,956
In 1, 2, 3.

679
00:25:25,858 --> 00:25:26,658
In 1, 2, 3.

680
00:25:27,726 --> 00:25:30,027
(The two are
effortlessly adorable together.)

681
00:25:30,028 --> 00:25:30,795
That turned out well.

682
00:25:34,266 --> 00:25:36,167
(Poking)

683
00:25:37,937 --> 00:25:38,837
In 1, 2, 3.

684
00:25:38,838 --> 00:25:40,839
Oh, my goodness.

685
00:25:41,941 --> 00:25:43,275
Come forward.

686
00:25:43,276 --> 00:25:45,010
Should we just take one without any pose?

687
00:25:49,415 --> 00:25:50,315
(Glaring)

688
00:25:50,316 --> 00:25:51,283
(Surprised)

689
00:25:51,850 --> 00:25:55,619
(The closer Jin Woo gets,
the more flustered Jin Young becomes.)

690
00:25:55,888 --> 00:25:58,823
Honestly, I thought
he was incredibly handsome...

691
00:25:58,924 --> 00:26:01,560
from the very beginning.

692
00:26:01,561 --> 00:26:03,861
I even thought he looked like an idol.

693
00:26:03,862 --> 00:26:06,230
I'd be lying if I said
I didn't feel butterflies.

694
00:26:07,032 --> 00:26:08,766
Jin Woo's face is his greatest weapon.

695
00:26:10,669 --> 00:26:11,469
What pose should we do?

696
00:26:13,806 --> 00:26:14,606
Think of one.

697
00:26:15,341 --> 00:26:16,274
Think.

698
00:26:16,275 --> 00:26:17,575
(Staring)

699
00:26:18,511 --> 00:26:19,377
What should we do?

700
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,480
(Getting close)

701
00:26:23,248 --> 00:26:24,381
Gosh.

702
00:26:24,850 --> 00:26:27,118
(Frozen)

703
00:26:27,586 --> 00:26:28,886
You're the one who picked this pose.

704
00:26:28,988 --> 00:26:31,389
- We had to take something somehow,
- You chose it.

705
00:26:31,533 --> 00:26:33,968
so I just went with it.

706
00:26:33,993 --> 00:26:34,993
Okay.

707
00:26:36,595 --> 00:26:39,630
(There's an awkward tension
between the two.)

708
00:26:39,631 --> 00:26:42,967
Jin Woo suddenly got
really forward with me.

709
00:26:43,102 --> 00:26:45,570
It made me wonder,
"What's going through his head?"

710
00:26:45,771 --> 00:26:48,806
I did feel butterflies a bit,
to be honest,

711
00:26:48,807 --> 00:26:50,541
but everything happened so suddenly...

712
00:26:50,676 --> 00:26:52,477
that I kept thinking,

713
00:26:52,811 --> 00:26:55,713
"Why is he acting
like this all of a sudden?"

714
00:26:56,381 --> 00:26:58,383
I was actually trying
to focus my feelings on Jung Won,

715
00:26:58,384 --> 00:27:00,518
so part of me felt...

716
00:27:01,354 --> 00:27:02,320
that...

717
00:27:03,290 --> 00:27:05,523
Jin Woo shouldn't
suddenly come on so strong.

718
00:27:06,126 --> 00:27:08,793
But he's seriously so handsome.

719
00:27:09,494 --> 00:27:10,395
He really is.

720
00:27:11,130 --> 00:27:11,963
It's almost unfair.

721
00:27:12,998 --> 00:27:16,500
I think she was probably wondering...

722
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:19,737
whether the poses
and things I did during the photo shoot...

723
00:27:19,805 --> 00:27:23,074
felt like a romantic move,

724
00:27:23,075 --> 00:27:25,343
or whether I was just doing them for fun.

725
00:27:26,813 --> 00:27:30,314
Well, it's not like Jin Young...

726
00:27:30,616 --> 00:27:35,186
suddenly became the person I was
most interested in overnight.

727
00:27:35,387 --> 00:27:38,189
I think that would've been
too sudden a change in my feelings.

728
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:43,394
I approached Jin Young
with about 30 percent romantic interest,

729
00:27:43,728 --> 00:27:47,131
and through that process, I realized
I was starting to see her romantically.

730
00:27:47,132 --> 00:27:50,668
At the same time,
I found her really fun to be around...

731
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,770
and a genuinely nice person.

732
00:27:53,505 --> 00:27:58,943
(What change will
Jin Woo's straightforward approach bring?)

733
00:27:59,178 --> 00:28:01,045
- Let's go in.
- Bye. Great job today.

734
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:02,081
- Good night.
- Bye.

735
00:28:02,781 --> 00:28:03,548
See you tomorrow.

736
00:28:03,549 --> 00:28:05,750
- Good job. Good night.
- Good night.

737
00:28:11,690 --> 00:28:13,625
(Si Won looks through the photos
he took with Yu Jin.)

738
00:28:13,626 --> 00:28:15,359
Oh, he's looking at the photos again.

739
00:28:18,497 --> 00:28:20,098
(Giggling)

740
00:28:20,099 --> 00:28:21,987
Si Won must've been really happy.

741
00:28:21,988 --> 00:28:23,502
(Just looking at them brings
a smile to his face.)

742
00:28:24,770 --> 00:28:29,440
(Si Won reminisces about his time
with Yu Jin.)

743
00:28:34,079 --> 00:28:35,780
(The plushie Si Won won for Yu Jin)

744
00:28:35,781 --> 00:28:37,481
Look at how tightly she's hugging
that plushie.

745
00:28:38,217 --> 00:28:41,119
The typical behavior of those who have
just come back from a date!

746
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,487
(Yu Jin thinks about her time
with Si Won.)

747
00:28:43,622 --> 00:28:45,823
- See you at ten.
- See you.

748
00:28:45,824 --> 00:28:47,291
Bye!

749
00:28:47,292 --> 00:28:48,192
Good night.

750
00:28:49,495 --> 00:28:50,395
Si Won.

751
00:28:51,964 --> 00:28:52,997
I'm back.

752
00:28:54,032 --> 00:28:54,798
Brother.

753
00:28:55,434 --> 00:28:57,001
- Did you have fun?
- I'm back.

754
00:28:57,035 --> 00:28:57,935
Did you have fun?

755
00:28:58,103 --> 00:29:00,038
- Those two are both on cloud nine.
- It's game over.

756
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:01,806
This room is the winners' room.

757
00:29:01,807 --> 00:29:03,407
It's a full-on celebration in here.

758
00:29:03,408 --> 00:29:05,409
I wish the people in these rooms would
go on a double date together.

759
00:29:08,047 --> 00:29:10,514
How was it? Your
date with Jin Young and Yu Jin.

760
00:29:10,749 --> 00:29:11,449
Did you have fun?

761
00:29:11,617 --> 00:29:14,551
- It was way more fun than I expected.
- Really?

762
00:29:16,555 --> 00:29:17,855
I had such a great time today.

763
00:29:17,956 --> 00:29:20,291
I can tell by the look on your face.

764
00:29:20,292 --> 00:29:20,958
Really?

765
00:29:21,293 --> 00:29:23,027
I've never seen
Si Won react like this before.

766
00:29:24,763 --> 00:29:28,432
(As soon as she gets back to the house,
Jin Young heads somewhere.)

767
00:29:29,268 --> 00:29:30,601
Jin Young, go shake things up.

768
00:29:31,803 --> 00:29:32,903
Si Won,

769
00:29:33,972 --> 00:29:34,972
ask Jung Won to come out for me.

770
00:29:35,174 --> 00:29:37,341
She must've really wanted to see him.

771
00:29:37,743 --> 00:29:41,112
Jung Won,
someone's asking for you outside.

772
00:29:41,113 --> 00:29:41,846
Okay.

773
00:29:43,015 --> 00:29:43,814
Is it Jin Young out there?

774
00:29:44,149 --> 00:29:44,915
Yes.

775
00:29:46,818 --> 00:29:48,886
(Learning that Jin Young is outside,
Jin Woo immediately heads out.)

776
00:29:48,887 --> 00:29:49,987
Jin Woo is going out?

777
00:29:50,322 --> 00:29:51,656
She asked for Jung Won.

778
00:29:53,425 --> 00:29:54,492
Jin Young.

779
00:29:55,594 --> 00:29:56,528
During the interview...

780
00:29:56,529 --> 00:29:58,129
(Jin Woo hands her the photos
they took together.)

781
00:29:58,564 --> 00:30:00,630
You wouldn't want these photos
sitting around in our room, right?

782
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:04,166
(Jung Won comes out immediately.)

783
00:30:04,466 --> 00:30:05,933
(Peeking)

784
00:30:06,633 --> 00:30:09,333
(Jung Won notices Jin Woo is
with Jin Young.)

785
00:30:09,933 --> 00:30:12,365
I don't want Jung Won
to see this right now.

786
00:30:12,366 --> 00:30:13,632
- Really?
- Do you want to keep it, then?

787
00:30:13,633 --> 00:30:15,199
No, you can keep it.

788
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:17,400
But I don't want you to show it to him.

789
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:19,700
Jin Young is really clear
about everything, isn't she?

790
00:30:20,333 --> 00:30:22,533
- I'll hide it, then.
- Okay.

791
00:30:23,766 --> 00:30:24,665
You can tell me anything.

792
00:30:24,666 --> 00:30:26,933
- Can I just tell you random things?
- Yes.

793
00:30:27,466 --> 00:30:28,565
He's hurt.

794
00:30:28,566 --> 00:30:29,600
(Jin Young didn't want
Jung Won to see the photo.)

795
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,132
She doesn't want Jung Won
to see the picture.

796
00:30:32,133 --> 00:30:34,632
And she wants him
to hide it from Jung Won.

797
00:30:34,633 --> 00:30:36,166
But what if Jin Woo...

798
00:30:37,166 --> 00:30:38,133
He understood, right?

799
00:30:38,466 --> 00:30:40,432
After she said that,

800
00:30:40,433 --> 00:30:43,000
what if Jin Woo put it
on Jung Won's pillow?

801
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:45,366
(Evil smile)

802
00:30:46,733 --> 00:30:49,866
(Jin Young and Jung Won come
to the common area for a conversation.)

803
00:30:50,833 --> 00:30:54,566
(This is the first conversation
between these two today.)

804
00:30:56,166 --> 00:30:57,566
(Staring)

805
00:30:57,666 --> 00:30:58,966
Who did your hair today?

806
00:30:59,466 --> 00:31:00,400
My hair?

807
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:02,532
Guess who.

808
00:31:02,533 --> 00:31:03,565
What?

809
00:31:03,566 --> 00:31:04,665
I think you did.

810
00:31:04,666 --> 00:31:05,500
I did.

811
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,700
Who else would do my hair except me?

812
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:10,866
- Don't you think?
- You're right.

813
00:31:12,166 --> 00:31:13,600
I need to trim my fingernails.

814
00:31:14,533 --> 00:31:16,300
Your nails are already very short.

815
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,999
It'd be painful
if you trimmed them too short, right?

816
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,132
Goodness.

817
00:31:20,133 --> 00:31:22,700
They're already short.
What more is there to trim?

818
00:31:23,233 --> 00:31:24,865
I can just trim them a little more.

819
00:31:24,866 --> 00:31:28,833
- So you never leave any white part?
- I guess not.

820
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:34,166
(Everyone gathers
in the common area one by one.)

821
00:31:34,700 --> 00:31:36,400
(Peeking)

822
00:31:37,133 --> 00:31:38,765
The big sister is coming.

823
00:31:38,766 --> 00:31:41,299
Ji Hye really does look
like a fitting model.

824
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:43,532
Watching her take pictures today,
I understood why she could be a model.

825
00:31:43,533 --> 00:31:44,333
She's good.

826
00:31:45,466 --> 00:31:46,366
Oh...

827
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:47,900
Hello.

828
00:31:49,033 --> 00:31:51,133
(Finding her cute)

829
00:31:51,466 --> 00:31:52,433
Oh, no.

830
00:31:52,966 --> 00:31:54,765
- She's different.
- She's a pro.

831
00:31:54,766 --> 00:31:55,699
- Of course.
- You're a model, right?

832
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:57,000
How long do you think I've been modeling?

833
00:31:57,266 --> 00:31:58,565
What an expert.

834
00:31:58,566 --> 00:31:59,666
(Laughing)

835
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:03,333
(Ji Hye and Jung Won seem
very close after the date.)

836
00:32:05,533 --> 00:32:08,966
(Jun Han and Yu Jin also come
into the common area.)

837
00:32:09,366 --> 00:32:11,466
(Peeking)

838
00:32:12,466 --> 00:32:14,866
(Si Won moves his seat
after spotting Yu Jin.)

839
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:16,032
I want to sit next to you.

840
00:32:16,033 --> 00:32:17,100
- I want to sit here.
- Okay.

841
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:20,665
(He pushes Yun So away...)

842
00:32:20,666 --> 00:32:24,000
(to make space for Yu Jin to sit.)

843
00:32:24,866 --> 00:32:27,299
(During the job reveal...)

844
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:29,365
(and last night,)

845
00:32:29,366 --> 00:32:30,199
Wait!

846
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,833
(Yu Jin has always been sitting
in the corner.)

847
00:32:33,300 --> 00:32:34,432
(Si Won saves Yu Jin's spot.)

848
00:32:34,433 --> 00:32:36,332
Because Yu Jin loves that corner,

849
00:32:36,333 --> 00:32:38,533
he moves there to sit with her.

850
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:41,200
(As Yu Jin comes in...)

851
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:43,566
(Peeking)

852
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:46,600
It's been a while
since I last saw you, Yu Jin.

853
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:49,333
(Yu Jin comes over next to Si Won,
just as he expected.)

854
00:32:50,733 --> 00:32:53,299
- That's so sweet.
- He's cute.

855
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:54,166
The picture of us.

856
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:56,733
- I brought it to show it off to everyone.
- We took a picture together.

857
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,700
- Let me see!
- Let me see it.

858
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:01,966
Our picture is really cute.

859
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:04,366
It's a really good picture.

860
00:33:05,133 --> 00:33:07,265
- It really is a good one.
- So cute.

861
00:33:07,266 --> 00:33:09,266
- You're even in similar outfits.
- Right.

862
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:10,533
It's so good.

863
00:33:11,066 --> 00:33:12,499
The picture is so good.

864
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:13,632
(Ji Seung arrives.)

865
00:33:13,633 --> 00:33:16,466
- We're so cute.
- We really are.

866
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:19,633
(Ji Seung comes closer
to see the picture.)

867
00:33:20,233 --> 00:33:21,700
I told you we'd take the instant photo.

868
00:33:23,066 --> 00:33:24,733
(Flustered)

869
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:26,566
So cute.

870
00:33:27,666 --> 00:33:29,933
Yu Jin, you look so cute in this one.

871
00:33:30,966 --> 00:33:33,233
Si Won is really handsome, isn't he?

872
00:33:33,833 --> 00:33:35,433
You're really pretty.

873
00:33:37,500 --> 00:33:42,500
(Ji Seung quietly leaves the spot.)

874
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:47,000
Yun So, can you make a finger heart
when you take a photo?

875
00:33:47,333 --> 00:33:48,632
- Can I make this sign?
- Of course he can.

876
00:33:48,633 --> 00:33:49,500
I can.

877
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:51,365
You should
at least make a cheek heart too.

878
00:33:51,366 --> 00:33:53,199
(It bothers Si Won that he couldn't
make a cute pose while taking photos.)

879
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,465
That's the minimum, right?

880
00:33:54,466 --> 00:33:56,132
You should at least make a cheek heart.

881
00:33:56,133 --> 00:33:57,600
- A cheek heart?
- Can you do it now?

882
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:01,933
Of course I can do it now.

883
00:34:03,800 --> 00:34:04,666
That's crazy.

884
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,933
(Cute)

885
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:13,000
Joy and disappointment collide.

886
00:34:13,633 --> 00:34:16,200
After the date,
the two seemed really close.

887
00:34:16,633 --> 00:34:18,500
It bothers me a little.

888
00:34:19,533 --> 00:34:23,500
Si Won might have had a change of heart.

889
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:32,165
- Do you want to go out?
- Let's go out.

890
00:34:32,166 --> 00:34:33,233
Let's eat this outside.

891
00:34:35,033 --> 00:34:37,465
This is so romantic!

892
00:34:37,466 --> 00:34:38,900
The place is amazing.

893
00:34:40,433 --> 00:34:42,532
(Jung Won and Jin Young sit
next to each other.)

894
00:34:42,533 --> 00:34:45,966
You're wearing the thickest clothes,
a padded coat.

895
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,966
Jin Young, can I have a moment with you?

896
00:34:51,033 --> 00:34:53,733
(Turning his head around)

897
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:55,199
Are you drunk?

898
00:34:55,200 --> 00:34:56,200
No, I'm not.

899
00:34:57,166 --> 00:34:58,832
You turned as red as a carrot.

900
00:34:58,833 --> 00:35:00,065
No, I'm not drunk.

901
00:35:00,066 --> 00:35:00,932
Not at all?

902
00:35:00,933 --> 00:35:01,866
Maybe about ten percent?

903
00:35:02,566 --> 00:35:04,266
- How much did you drink?
- A couple of shots of soju?

904
00:35:05,366 --> 00:35:07,165
- I'm not drunk.
- You drank two shots?

905
00:35:07,166 --> 00:35:08,133
Two or three?

906
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:13,933
(Jin Young enters Jin Woo's room.)

907
00:35:15,233 --> 00:35:16,333
You're sitting in the spot
where you sat yesterday.

908
00:35:17,166 --> 00:35:20,933
(They face each other in the same spot
where they talked last night.)

909
00:35:22,266 --> 00:35:23,400
What are they going to talk about?

910
00:35:24,166 --> 00:35:29,333
Yesterday, I talked things
over with you, right?

911
00:35:29,900 --> 00:35:32,833
And today, it was a date.

912
00:35:33,333 --> 00:35:36,432
As your date today, I did my best.

913
00:35:36,433 --> 00:35:39,799
But I couldn't act like your boyfriend
after just one night, right?

914
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,432
So I fooled around a lot on purpose.

915
00:35:41,433 --> 00:35:43,799
- Oh, did you?
- If I crossed...

916
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:46,865
any line, I'm sorry.

917
00:35:46,866 --> 00:35:48,633
No, you didn't do anything wrong.

918
00:35:49,066 --> 00:35:53,333
Anyway, although it wasn't
a 1-on-1 date with you today,

919
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:57,400
I tried my best to be romantic with you.

920
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,066
And I feel...

921
00:36:01,766 --> 00:36:04,200
the most comfortable around you.

922
00:36:04,766 --> 00:36:05,766
I'm attracted to you.

923
00:36:08,433 --> 00:36:10,533
That's why I called you here,
to hear what you think.

924
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:13,333
He's so straightforward.

925
00:36:13,334 --> 00:36:14,277
(She hesitates to answer.)

926
00:36:14,833 --> 00:36:16,500
(Nervous)

927
00:36:18,333 --> 00:36:21,632
Actually, in the first interview
when I had just arrived here,

928
00:36:21,633 --> 00:36:22,565
I said Jun Han was first,

929
00:36:22,566 --> 00:36:24,099
and you were second.

930
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:26,965
I told them that Jin Woo was so handsome.

931
00:36:26,966 --> 00:36:28,532
- On the day you arrived?
- Yes.

932
00:36:28,533 --> 00:36:31,766
You were so handsome
that I couldn't look into your eyes.

933
00:36:32,866 --> 00:36:35,700
But time passed so quickly.

934
00:36:36,133 --> 00:36:41,199
And now, I'm the most attracted
to Jung Won right now.

935
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:42,900
He makes me feel romantic.

936
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:44,966
So...

937
00:36:45,666 --> 00:36:47,532
Oh, no.

938
00:36:47,533 --> 00:36:52,432
I want to focus on the person
I care about the most.

939
00:36:52,433 --> 00:36:54,432
- Because we're almost out of time.
- Right.

940
00:36:54,433 --> 00:36:58,100
It doesn't matter to me who you like
the most or the second most.

941
00:36:59,433 --> 00:37:03,333
I know you've been building
relationships with others.

942
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:06,833
But rather than that,

943
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,832
I just want to keep asking you out...

944
00:37:08,833 --> 00:37:10,299
if you see me as a man.

945
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:12,865
That's what I want to do.

946
00:37:12,866 --> 00:37:15,065
What should I do? Seriously.

947
00:37:15,066 --> 00:37:16,465
Is it because you feel sorry for me?

948
00:37:16,466 --> 00:37:18,133
No. Geez. What should I do?

949
00:37:22,408 --> 00:37:25,675
It's not that I don't see you as a man.

950
00:37:25,699 --> 00:37:28,165
But the timing isn't good right now.

951
00:37:28,166 --> 00:37:30,749
And I've made up my mind...

952
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:35,199
that I'll focus only on the person
I care about the most.

953
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:37,566
- That's what I'll do.
- I understand.

954
00:37:38,633 --> 00:37:41,665
So I don't want to lead you on.

955
00:37:41,666 --> 00:37:42,833
You're not.

956
00:37:43,500 --> 00:37:45,800
But about that timing,

957
00:37:46,166 --> 00:37:47,500
from my point of view...

958
00:37:48,266 --> 00:37:50,233
- Is that misleading too?
- No, it's not.

959
00:37:50,666 --> 00:37:53,499
But I think it's something I can change.

960
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:55,932
It's not you misleading me.

961
00:37:55,933 --> 00:37:57,366
It's me wanting to do something about it.

962
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,900
It's not like my heart
didn't flutter today.

963
00:38:05,833 --> 00:38:08,433
Of course, I found it somewhat romantic.

964
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:11,733
Especially, I've been thinking
that you're really handsome,

965
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:14,132
- and you made...
- I made my moves?

966
00:38:14,133 --> 00:38:15,300
Yes, you did.

967
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,699
I was thrown off.

968
00:38:17,700 --> 00:38:19,565
- "Is he crazy?"
- Like, "What's going on?"

969
00:38:19,566 --> 00:38:21,199
"Is he crazy?"

970
00:38:21,200 --> 00:38:24,065
- But...
- Where? When did you feel that?

971
00:38:24,066 --> 00:38:25,533
Did I go that far?

972
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,233
When we took the pictures?

973
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:30,666
- Or before?
- No. Your problem is your face.

974
00:38:31,133 --> 00:38:32,433
That's your biggest problem.

975
00:38:33,266 --> 00:38:36,066
Anyway, you have that handsome face
as your weapon.

976
00:38:36,700 --> 00:38:39,166
However...

977
00:38:40,600 --> 00:38:41,600
No.

978
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:44,132
Do I have to keep listening?

979
00:38:44,133 --> 00:38:45,532
Your heart pounded today
because of me anyway.

980
00:38:45,533 --> 00:38:47,365
- Yes, it did.
- That means you see me as a man.

981
00:38:47,366 --> 00:38:49,065
- That's true, but...
- But?

982
00:38:49,066 --> 00:38:52,300
But if I keep leading you on,

983
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:56,900
I don't think I'll be able to focus
because it'll be too confusing for me.

984
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,333
So you want me to stop?

985
00:38:59,533 --> 00:39:02,732
But what if I don't want to?

986
00:39:02,733 --> 00:39:04,032
What if I don't want that?

987
00:39:04,033 --> 00:39:06,832
No, I mean... Anyway.

988
00:39:06,833 --> 00:39:08,599
(Broken)

989
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:09,566
I mean...

990
00:39:09,933 --> 00:39:11,765
Hey!

991
00:39:11,766 --> 00:39:12,800
She can't hide it.

992
00:39:13,866 --> 00:39:15,200
I can still ask you out, right?

993
00:39:15,533 --> 00:39:17,966
- That's up to you.
- Right.

994
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:21,732
(Jin Woo makes a move toward Jin Young.)

995
00:39:21,733 --> 00:39:24,799
(Where will their relationship go
from here?)

996
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:27,232
Today's date wasn't bad at all.

997
00:39:27,233 --> 00:39:28,666
- No, it wasn't.
- So...

998
00:39:29,333 --> 00:39:31,500
How about we all root for Jin Woo?

999
00:39:31,866 --> 00:39:33,865
I just want the two of them to work out.

1000
00:39:33,866 --> 00:39:37,766
For now, I think we should keep
our eyes on them from here.

1001
00:39:39,527 --> 00:39:41,233
I should've grabbed my coat.

1002
00:39:44,133 --> 00:39:45,232
It's so cold out here.

1003
00:39:45,233 --> 00:39:46,500
Is it? Did you have a good conversation?

1004
00:39:46,733 --> 00:39:47,566
Yes.

1005
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:50,066
What is it?

1006
00:39:50,433 --> 00:39:52,433
What is it about?

1007
00:39:55,233 --> 00:39:56,566
Pandora's QR?

1008
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:58,965
(Pandora's QR is now open.)

1009
00:39:58,966 --> 00:40:01,200
"Scan the QR code
of the person you're curious about..."

1010
00:40:01,266 --> 00:40:03,934
"and you can check their top picks
so far?"

1011
00:40:03,935 --> 00:40:05,704
(If you scan the QR code
of the person you're curious about,)

1012
00:40:05,705 --> 00:40:07,171
(you'll be able to check
their top picks so far.)

1013
00:40:07,172 --> 00:40:09,073
It disappears in an hour.

1014
00:40:09,774 --> 00:40:10,707
- All their top picks?
- From Day One?

1015
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:13,110
- Every night.
- All their top picks from Day One.

1016
00:40:13,111 --> 00:40:13,910
Their top picks?

1017
00:40:14,078 --> 00:40:16,312
You should start running now.

1018
00:40:16,348 --> 00:40:17,414
I'd never check that.

1019
00:40:17,415 --> 00:40:18,381
- No?
- I wouldn't either.

1020
00:40:18,382 --> 00:40:19,149
I would never.

1021
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:21,518
Who do you think would check whose QR?

1022
00:40:21,519 --> 00:40:24,521
Jin Young and Ji Hye would
check Jung Won's.

1023
00:40:24,522 --> 00:40:25,688
Yun So...

1024
00:40:26,925 --> 00:40:28,259
would check Ju Hee's...

1025
00:40:28,526 --> 00:40:30,026
and start getting rid of them.

1026
00:40:30,261 --> 00:40:31,395
- With force?
- Yes.

1027
00:40:31,396 --> 00:40:33,330
He might push one into a pool.

1028
00:40:34,165 --> 00:40:36,166
He'd give them
the same hairstyle overnight.

1029
00:40:37,502 --> 00:40:41,004
(The QR Room is open again.)

1030
00:40:43,641 --> 00:40:49,179
(You can see who your crush picked
every night.)

1031
00:40:50,014 --> 00:40:54,651
(Who will open Pandora's box?)

1032
00:40:54,652 --> 00:40:56,186
- My gosh.
- It will disappear in an hour?

1033
00:40:56,187 --> 00:40:57,554
It disappears in an hour.

1034
00:40:57,555 --> 00:40:58,888
(Checking is optional.)

1035
00:40:58,889 --> 00:41:01,591
They gave them enough time
so they can check in secret too.

1036
00:41:02,494 --> 00:41:03,460
This is epic.

1037
00:41:04,329 --> 00:41:06,965
"Checking is optional."
I never check something like this.

1038
00:41:06,966 --> 00:41:08,565
I don't open Pandora's box.

1039
00:41:08,566 --> 00:41:10,334
- Right.
- That's cool.

1040
00:41:11,636 --> 00:41:14,871
Seeing that would make me feel uneasy.

1041
00:41:15,106 --> 00:41:16,106
- I...
- I won't check either.

1042
00:41:17,909 --> 00:41:18,742
Do you want to see it?

1043
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:20,010
I'll open it.

1044
00:41:23,548 --> 00:41:24,615
I knew it.

1045
00:41:25,284 --> 00:41:26,617
I knew you'd open that.

1046
00:41:27,719 --> 00:41:28,953
(Glancing)

1047
00:41:31,589 --> 00:41:32,589
I'll open it.

1048
00:41:35,927 --> 00:41:37,828
If you want to check, you should go now.

1049
00:41:37,829 --> 00:41:38,795
That wouldn't be bad.

1050
00:41:38,796 --> 00:41:39,963
If you don't want to, don't go.

1051
00:41:41,899 --> 00:41:44,768
(Looking around)

1052
00:41:45,304 --> 00:41:46,303
I'll go open it.

1053
00:41:48,706 --> 00:41:50,974
(Ji Hye gets up right away.)

1054
00:41:50,975 --> 00:41:51,908
There she goes.

1055
00:41:52,210 --> 00:41:54,378
- She's going to open Pandora's box.
- There goes Ji Hye!

1056
00:41:54,379 --> 00:41:55,479
Ji Hye is going.

1057
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,713
- Go!
- Go!

1058
00:41:56,714 --> 00:41:57,681
I'll be back.

1059
00:42:03,221 --> 00:42:05,422
(Going to the QR Room without hesitation)

1060
00:42:06,791 --> 00:42:08,425
I wanted to open it immediately.

1061
00:42:08,826 --> 00:42:10,326
I was curious.

1062
00:42:10,395 --> 00:42:13,197
I wondered the person I was into...

1063
00:42:13,198 --> 00:42:15,799
had been choosing.

1064
00:42:16,968 --> 00:42:20,404
I thought it could help me...

1065
00:42:20,405 --> 00:42:22,039
make up my mind.

1066
00:42:22,774 --> 00:42:25,509
- Does it matter that much?
- It's important to her.

1067
00:42:25,510 --> 00:42:27,111
- Is it that important?
- Yes.

1068
00:42:27,211 --> 00:42:29,480
She can just go for the person she likes,
can't she?

1069
00:42:29,481 --> 00:42:32,081
Some people go
for the person they're into,

1070
00:42:32,082 --> 00:42:34,784
while others prefer someone
who's into them too.

1071
00:42:36,988 --> 00:42:41,325
(Which younger man's feelings
does Ji Hye want to be sure of?)

1072
00:42:41,926 --> 00:42:45,795
(The first person to face Pandora QRs)

1073
00:42:47,031 --> 00:42:48,732
(Swiping)

1074
00:42:49,434 --> 00:42:52,269
(The person Ji Hye is curious about)

1075
00:42:53,171 --> 00:42:54,338
(The Pandora QR that Ji Hye opened is...)

1076
00:42:54,339 --> 00:42:55,205
It must be Jung Won, right?

1077
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:57,473
(Jung Won's.)

1078
00:42:57,474 --> 00:42:58,708
I knew Ji Hye would choose that.

1079
00:42:59,410 --> 00:43:02,712
(Who has Jin Won been into every night?)

1080
00:43:03,448 --> 00:43:05,582
(Frowning)

1081
00:43:07,652 --> 00:43:10,053
(Day 2: Ji Hye)

1082
00:43:10,054 --> 00:43:13,290
(Day 3: Jin Young, Day 4: Jin Young)

1083
00:43:13,291 --> 00:43:14,992
(Except for the first day,
Jung Young has been choosing Jin Young.)

1084
00:43:14,993 --> 00:43:16,894
That might be a bit of a blow.

1085
00:43:19,597 --> 00:43:22,599
He's been choosing Jin Young
except for his first day.

1086
00:43:23,167 --> 00:43:26,636
Actually, I thought about it a lot
after the amusement park.

1087
00:43:26,637 --> 00:43:28,440
I was worried...

1088
00:43:28,441 --> 00:43:32,509
that Jung Won might just think
that I'm a fun older woman.

1089
00:43:32,510 --> 00:43:34,511
Did I make myself come across that way?

1090
00:43:35,613 --> 00:43:37,814
Have I been doing it wrong?

1091
00:43:38,182 --> 00:43:39,582
I kept wondering.

1092
00:43:39,951 --> 00:43:41,485
But after checking his QR,

1093
00:43:42,086 --> 00:43:44,054
I realized I was right.

1094
00:43:44,856 --> 00:43:46,356
Jung Won only sees me...

1095
00:43:46,357 --> 00:43:50,127
as someone who is fun
and easy to be around.

1096
00:43:50,895 --> 00:43:53,430
If Jin Young likes him,

1097
00:43:54,399 --> 00:43:55,432
I should let him go.

1098
00:43:57,969 --> 00:44:03,006
(Will Ji Hye give up Jung Won like this?)

1099
00:44:03,284 --> 00:44:06,509
I'll go after Ji Hye.

1100
00:44:06,577 --> 00:44:07,744
Really? Do you want to check?

1101
00:44:09,213 --> 00:44:10,714
I never open Pandora's box.

1102
00:44:10,715 --> 00:44:12,048
- Me neither.
- I wouldn't bother.

1103
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:14,450
What matters is the end.

1104
00:44:14,713 --> 00:44:17,588
I just want to satisfy my curiosity.

1105
00:44:18,756 --> 00:44:19,622
I get it.

1106
00:44:24,595 --> 00:44:26,129
I'll be back.

1107
00:44:27,532 --> 00:44:28,799
She looks happy.

1108
00:44:28,800 --> 00:44:29,900
Do you feel better?

1109
00:44:30,034 --> 00:44:30,834
Yes!

1110
00:44:31,269 --> 00:44:33,003
I wonder whose QR she opened.

1111
00:44:33,204 --> 00:44:34,070
I won't tell you.

1112
00:44:34,739 --> 00:44:35,539
(Sassy)

1113
00:44:38,743 --> 00:44:44,114
(Jin Young arrived to check Pandora QRs.)

1114
00:44:44,482 --> 00:44:46,750
(Looking around)

1115
00:44:47,151 --> 00:44:49,419
(Smiling)

1116
00:44:50,021 --> 00:44:54,524
(The person Jin Young is curious about...)

1117
00:44:54,525 --> 00:44:55,726
(is Jin Young as expected.)

1118
00:44:55,727 --> 00:44:57,494
She only has eyes for him.

1119
00:45:00,631 --> 00:45:03,566
(Smiling)

1120
00:45:04,702 --> 00:45:06,603
She saw Jung Won's QR.

1121
00:45:06,971 --> 00:45:08,405
To be honest, I was a little surprised.

1122
00:45:08,406 --> 00:45:10,640
When I saw it, I was like, "What?"

1123
00:45:11,742 --> 00:45:14,143
(Day 2: Ji Hye,
Day 3: Jin Young, Day 4: Jin Young)

1124
00:45:14,144 --> 00:45:17,180
He's been choosing me
since we played Truth Game.

1125
00:45:17,448 --> 00:45:19,516
During that game,

1126
00:45:19,951 --> 00:45:22,519
he kept choosing Ji Hye as his number one.

1127
00:45:23,955 --> 00:45:27,858
(Say something heart-fluttering
to your number one.)

1128
00:45:28,003 --> 00:45:29,459
I had a lot of fun today.

1129
00:45:30,128 --> 00:45:33,831
(Jung Won chose Ji Hye as his top pick
during Truth Game.)

1130
00:45:33,832 --> 00:45:34,865
That's true.

1131
00:45:36,434 --> 00:45:40,904
So I don't know why he sent me his QR.

1132
00:45:40,905 --> 00:45:42,472
Why did he choose me?

1133
00:45:43,075 --> 00:45:44,842
I wanted to ask him why.

1134
00:45:44,843 --> 00:45:46,176
I was so curious.

1135
00:45:47,174 --> 00:45:48,461
And I'm kind of touched.

1136
00:45:51,182 --> 00:45:56,620
(Jin Young is touched and also curious
at the same time.)

1137
00:45:57,388 --> 00:45:58,922
(Smiling)

1138
00:45:58,923 --> 00:46:00,423
It made me like Jung Won more.

1139
00:46:01,759 --> 00:46:02,559
She's happy.

1140
00:46:05,429 --> 00:46:07,764
Now that I think about it,

1141
00:46:07,765 --> 00:46:10,166
we don't really know how Jung Won feels.

1142
00:46:10,167 --> 00:46:10,900
Right.

1143
00:46:11,302 --> 00:46:13,770
Their love triangle is still unclear.

1144
00:46:14,405 --> 00:46:17,941
(After checking Jung Won's Pandora QR,)

1145
00:46:17,942 --> 00:46:21,444
(Ji Hye seems to be lost in thought.)

1146
00:46:23,014 --> 00:46:24,014
I'm going to go over there.

1147
00:46:24,682 --> 00:46:25,615
- The QR Room?
- Yes.

1148
00:46:26,450 --> 00:46:27,750
- Are you going to open Pandora's box?
- Yes.

1149
00:46:29,754 --> 00:46:30,520
That's good.

1150
00:46:30,521 --> 00:46:31,154
(Nodding)

1151
00:46:31,322 --> 00:46:33,023
Jin Young's steps...

1152
00:46:33,024 --> 00:46:34,858
- Her steps look light.
- Is it light?

1153
00:46:34,993 --> 00:46:35,925
She looks cool.

1154
00:46:36,327 --> 00:46:38,895
(Relaxed?)

1155
00:46:39,230 --> 00:46:40,063
(Jin Young seems excited.)

1156
00:46:40,064 --> 00:46:42,065
- Show us again.
- That was cute.

1157
00:46:44,468 --> 00:46:46,669
- Why is she so cute?
- I know.

1158
00:46:46,670 --> 00:46:47,470
She's cute.

1159
00:46:48,239 --> 00:46:51,441
- Ji Hye must be annoyed.
- Look at her face.

1160
00:46:51,442 --> 00:46:53,043
- They saw the same thing.
- Yes.

1161
00:46:53,244 --> 00:46:55,345
She's coming back like, "I won."

1162
00:46:55,346 --> 00:46:56,813
Jung Won must be anxious.

1163
00:46:56,814 --> 00:46:59,583
He must be sweating everywhere.

1164
00:46:59,584 --> 00:47:01,318
His back and his armpits.

1165
00:47:01,852 --> 00:47:04,153
(Glancing over)

1166
00:47:04,522 --> 00:47:05,422
You can go now.

1167
00:47:05,423 --> 00:47:06,189
I'll be back.

1168
00:47:07,425 --> 00:47:08,191
He's fast.

1169
00:47:11,228 --> 00:47:16,099
(Whose Pandora QR will Jung Won open?)

1170
00:47:16,234 --> 00:47:17,401
Did you get your answers?

1171
00:47:17,536 --> 00:47:18,802
- What?
- Did you get your questions answered?

1172
00:47:20,738 --> 00:47:22,839
- Yes, I did!
- Because she opened it.

1173
00:47:24,842 --> 00:47:25,642
I feel good.

1174
00:47:28,913 --> 00:47:32,883
(Jung Won came running.)

1175
00:47:33,251 --> 00:47:34,718
Let me see.

1176
00:47:39,423 --> 00:47:43,159
Will Jung Won open Ji Hye's
or Jin Young's?

1177
00:47:45,029 --> 00:47:49,099
(Whose Pandora QR will Jung Won open?)

1178
00:47:49,100 --> 00:47:50,033
Is it Ji Hye's?

1179
00:47:51,202 --> 00:47:52,002
Whose QR will he open?

1180
00:47:52,003 --> 00:47:54,104
(Male Bombshell Jung Won's choice?)

1181
00:47:56,907 --> 00:47:59,776
(The Pandora QR that Jung Won opened...)

1182
00:47:59,777 --> 00:48:02,879
(belongs to Ji Hye.)

1183
00:48:06,717 --> 00:48:09,585
I'm into Jin Young,

1184
00:48:09,854 --> 00:48:11,655
but I wanted to see Ji Hye's.

1185
00:48:12,723 --> 00:48:15,525
I wanted to know something
that would give me clarity.

1186
00:48:16,694 --> 00:48:19,863
If Ji Hye was never into me,

1187
00:48:20,398 --> 00:48:22,866
I would keep going for Jin Young.

1188
00:48:22,867 --> 00:48:25,268
But when I saw her Pandora QR...

1189
00:48:25,269 --> 00:48:27,003
Ji Hye's Pandora QR.

1190
00:48:27,004 --> 00:48:29,206
(Tilting his head)

1191
00:48:29,207 --> 00:48:31,775
(Day 1: Yun So, Day 2: Jung Won)

1192
00:48:31,776 --> 00:48:34,911
(Day 3: Jun Han, Day 4: Jung Won)

1193
00:48:34,912 --> 00:48:36,413
(Ji Hye chose Jung Won at the end.)

1194
00:48:36,414 --> 00:48:37,514
And she chose me.

1195
00:48:37,515 --> 00:48:40,617
(Ji Hye chose Jung Won at the end.)

1196
00:48:40,618 --> 00:48:42,352
I felt like...

1197
00:48:42,353 --> 00:48:45,555
my assumptions had been completely off.

1198
00:48:47,291 --> 00:48:49,092
I'm really confused.

1199
00:48:52,196 --> 00:48:56,499
(Learning about Ji Hye's choice
gives Jung Won a lot to think about.)

1200
00:48:58,469 --> 00:49:00,570
After seeing that,

1201
00:49:01,904 --> 00:49:03,906
Jung Won thinks Ji Hye is into him,

1202
00:49:03,907 --> 00:49:06,642
and he changes his mind and pursues her.

1203
00:49:06,643 --> 00:49:08,478
But after seeing his QR,

1204
00:49:08,479 --> 00:49:10,546
Ji Hye changes her mind.

1205
00:49:10,882 --> 00:49:12,282
Then they misunderstand each other again.

1206
00:49:12,883 --> 00:49:14,150
He shouldn't hesitate.

1207
00:49:14,552 --> 00:49:16,620
He should resolve this situation quickly.

1208
00:49:17,655 --> 00:49:20,123
Why does everyone look so serious
when they come back?

1209
00:49:20,124 --> 00:49:20,890
What's with everyone?

1210
00:49:22,560 --> 00:49:24,394
(Glancing over)

1211
00:49:25,396 --> 00:49:27,697
(Glancing)

1212
00:49:27,865 --> 00:49:31,033
How was it? Do you feel any different now?

1213
00:49:32,770 --> 00:49:34,437
I just had a question.

1214
00:49:35,973 --> 00:49:37,707
- Do you have more questions now?
- Did you get an answer?

1215
00:49:38,476 --> 00:49:39,209
Did you?

1216
00:49:41,378 --> 00:49:42,979
(Smiling)

1217
00:49:43,314 --> 00:49:44,014
No comment.

1218
00:49:45,883 --> 00:49:46,616
No comment.

1219
00:49:46,851 --> 00:49:48,251
This isn't something to bring up here.

1220
00:49:54,058 --> 00:49:55,525
Did you get to talk
to everyone you wanted to?

1221
00:49:56,461 --> 00:49:59,596
I think Jung Won did.

1222
00:50:00,233 --> 00:50:01,000
Well...

1223
00:50:01,323 --> 00:50:02,123
Almost?

1224
00:50:02,833 --> 00:50:03,700
Almost.

1225
00:50:05,633 --> 00:50:09,300
But even though I've talked to them,

1226
00:50:09,766 --> 00:50:12,199
I haven't actually been
on a proper date with them yet.

1227
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:13,933
Talking to someone and going on a date
can be completely different.

1228
00:50:14,166 --> 00:50:16,066
That's true, though.

1229
00:50:16,633 --> 00:50:20,300
Jin Young is probably wondering
if Jung Won is talking about her.

1230
00:50:20,566 --> 00:50:22,933
She's also trying to figure out
what he really means.

1231
00:50:23,766 --> 00:50:25,933
Then if you get a Date Choice Pass,
are you going to ask that person out?

1232
00:50:29,566 --> 00:50:30,366
I don't know.

1233
00:50:32,266 --> 00:50:33,199
You're so evasive.

1234
00:50:33,200 --> 00:50:35,299
- He's such a sly fox.
- He really is.

1235
00:50:35,300 --> 00:50:37,332
- He's a total bombshell.
- He is, for sure.

1236
00:50:37,333 --> 00:50:39,400
The bombshells really are different.

1237
00:50:40,166 --> 00:50:41,632
Right.

1238
00:50:41,633 --> 00:50:42,832
Ji Hye's mind must be all over the place,

1239
00:50:42,833 --> 00:50:44,032
The bombshells are different.

1240
00:50:44,033 --> 00:50:45,066
Did you get the answers
you were looking for?

1241
00:50:46,333 --> 00:50:48,065
It was pretty much what I expected.

1242
00:50:48,066 --> 00:50:48,966
Really?

1243
00:50:49,400 --> 00:50:50,366
It was exactly what you expected?

1244
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:53,399
- Pretty much...
- It was pretty much what I expected.

1245
00:50:53,400 --> 00:50:54,266
Is that so?

1246
00:50:55,100 --> 00:50:56,666
Just as I expected.

1247
00:50:58,866 --> 00:51:03,233
(Jung Won can't stop thinking
about Ji Hye's answer.)

1248
00:51:03,600 --> 00:51:04,400
No?

1249
00:51:05,933 --> 00:51:09,666
(Jung Won has no response.)

1250
00:51:10,133 --> 00:51:11,869
They can't go to sleep tonight.

1251
00:51:11,893 --> 00:51:12,903
If they do, it's game over.

1252
00:51:13,866 --> 00:51:14,800
Why are you so serious?

1253
00:51:15,366 --> 00:51:16,865
- I'm not.
- Really?

1254
00:51:16,866 --> 00:51:17,900
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

1255
00:51:21,366 --> 00:51:23,866
So the Pandora QR was meant
for these three all along.

1256
00:51:24,366 --> 00:51:25,965
So, how was everyone's group date today?

1257
00:51:25,966 --> 00:51:28,732
And after the group date?

1258
00:51:28,733 --> 00:51:30,700
- I had so much fun.
- Did it change how you feel?

1259
00:51:31,266 --> 00:51:33,333
Well,

1260
00:51:34,166 --> 00:51:35,299
it kind of...

1261
00:51:35,300 --> 00:51:37,365
Mine definitely changed today.

1262
00:51:37,366 --> 00:51:39,099
- Really?
- Seriously?

1263
00:51:39,100 --> 00:51:40,266
I'm sure of it.

1264
00:51:40,966 --> 00:51:42,866
Did your feelings become more certain,
or did they change?

1265
00:51:44,100 --> 00:51:45,200
They've become completely certain.

1266
00:51:45,766 --> 00:51:47,633
- After today's date.
- Really?

1267
00:51:48,500 --> 00:51:50,399
- After the group date?
- Sorry?

1268
00:51:50,400 --> 00:51:51,333
After the group date?

1269
00:51:52,133 --> 00:51:53,266
Yes.

1270
00:51:54,100 --> 00:51:56,832
I think she's saying it to Jung Won.

1271
00:51:56,833 --> 00:51:57,766
Right?

1272
00:51:58,633 --> 00:51:59,732
(Smiling)

1273
00:51:59,733 --> 00:52:00,966
Jung Won is happy.

1274
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:03,165
(Reading the room)

1275
00:52:03,166 --> 00:52:05,665
Looking through it is actually pretty fun.

1276
00:52:05,666 --> 00:52:06,900
- Really?
- It's so much fun.

1277
00:52:07,566 --> 00:52:09,333
Jin Young is...

1278
00:52:09,666 --> 00:52:11,829
saying that on purpose
to get under Ji Hye's skin.

1279
00:52:12,266 --> 00:52:13,699
So the choices we've made are in it?

1280
00:52:13,700 --> 00:52:14,633
Exactly.

1281
00:52:15,066 --> 00:52:16,199
I can't believe it's already day five.

1282
00:52:16,200 --> 00:52:18,233
It's only day four for the bombshells.

1283
00:52:19,700 --> 00:52:20,933
Have you checked the bombshells' QR too?

1284
00:52:27,300 --> 00:52:28,633
I got you!

1285
00:52:28,966 --> 00:52:30,866
What's gotten into Jin Young?

1286
00:52:31,166 --> 00:52:33,966
It's cute that she thinks
he checked out her QR.

1287
00:52:35,333 --> 00:52:38,255
(Jin Young is completely mistaken.)

1288
00:52:38,966 --> 00:52:44,000
(The two become lost in thought.)

1289
00:52:44,500 --> 00:52:47,366
(The older women and younger guys
move to the common area.)

1290
00:52:48,966 --> 00:52:51,166
Maybe I should go check the Pandora QR.
But I'm not so sure.

1291
00:52:51,533 --> 00:52:53,700
It's really just
about satisfying your curiosity.

1292
00:52:54,266 --> 00:52:55,233
I'm not that curious.

1293
00:52:55,500 --> 00:52:56,665
So, you're not curious about anyone?

1294
00:52:56,666 --> 00:52:57,832
That's not it.

1295
00:52:57,833 --> 00:52:59,832
Then what is it? What's going on?

1296
00:52:59,833 --> 00:53:00,600
Me?

1297
00:53:01,166 --> 00:53:02,346
Shall we step outside for a minute?

1298
00:53:04,166 --> 00:53:07,699
(Ji Seung steps outside
with Jin Young for the moment.)

1299
00:53:07,700 --> 00:53:09,599
Wait, Ji Seung and Jin Young
are going outside together?

1300
00:53:09,600 --> 00:53:11,599
It's great that Jung Won is left!

1301
00:53:11,600 --> 00:53:12,500
You're going out?

1302
00:53:12,525 --> 00:53:13,891
Yes.

1303
00:53:14,466 --> 00:53:15,965
Are you actually escorting her out?

1304
00:53:15,966 --> 00:53:17,132
I'm just going out...

1305
00:53:17,133 --> 00:53:18,866
to get some fresh air too.

1306
00:53:19,266 --> 00:53:20,633
I might check the Pandora QR,
or I might not.

1307
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:24,799
- Let's go out.
- And think about it.

1308
00:53:24,800 --> 00:53:26,804
I'm the type of person
who puts things off as long as I can.

1309
00:53:28,300 --> 00:53:30,100
Isn't this a huge opportunity
for Jung Won?

1310
00:53:30,466 --> 00:53:31,699
(An exchange of glances)

1311
00:53:31,700 --> 00:53:33,665
(Bursting into laughter)

1312
00:53:33,666 --> 00:53:34,765
I knew it.

1313
00:53:34,766 --> 00:53:35,566
Do you want to talk?

1314
00:53:35,800 --> 00:53:36,932
(Nodding)

1315
00:53:36,933 --> 00:53:37,733
Now?

1316
00:53:39,316 --> 00:53:41,552
(Ji Hye and Jung Won immediately get up.)

1317
00:53:43,466 --> 00:53:45,133
I was thinking that
I should have a conversation with you.

1318
00:53:49,300 --> 00:53:52,833
(The two opened each other's Pandora,
and now they start talking.)

1319
00:53:53,066 --> 00:53:54,132
Whose QR did you check today?

1320
00:53:54,133 --> 00:53:55,032
I checked yours.

1321
00:53:55,033 --> 00:53:56,700
- I checked yours too.
- Really?

1322
00:53:59,366 --> 00:54:03,800
(They both laugh at the same time,
feeling awkward.)

1323
00:54:04,133 --> 00:54:06,700
I checked yours because I was curious.

1324
00:54:08,900 --> 00:54:10,365
How do you feel now?

1325
00:54:10,366 --> 00:54:11,200
I don't know.

1326
00:54:12,400 --> 00:54:14,665
At first,
I was obviously interested in you.

1327
00:54:14,666 --> 00:54:17,600
But I thought you weren't
showing any interest in me at all.

1328
00:54:19,033 --> 00:54:20,966
Ji Hye is surprised since she thought
she had shown her feelings.

1329
00:54:21,733 --> 00:54:25,865
So I thought you weren't
showing your feelings toward me.

1330
00:54:25,866 --> 00:54:27,632
But you kept saying that you were
getting more certain about this person.

1331
00:54:27,633 --> 00:54:31,166
So I thought that person wasn't me.

1332
00:54:32,366 --> 00:54:35,833
And I chose Jin Young...

1333
00:54:36,400 --> 00:54:40,266
because she was much more direct with me.

1334
00:54:40,633 --> 00:54:43,832
You chose Jin Young for two days in a row.

1335
00:54:43,833 --> 00:54:45,800
I chose you on the first day,

1336
00:54:46,466 --> 00:54:47,999
and I chose Jin Young the other two days.

1337
00:54:48,000 --> 00:54:50,532
So I thought, "What I thought was right."

1338
00:54:50,533 --> 00:54:55,800
I thought you only saw me
as a funny and comfortable older woman.

1339
00:54:57,533 --> 00:55:00,100
If I had been certain
about my feelings for Jin Young,

1340
00:55:00,766 --> 00:55:02,766
would I have checked your QR?
Think about it.

1341
00:55:03,500 --> 00:55:04,632
If I'd been so certain about her.

1342
00:55:04,633 --> 00:55:06,799
I thought you would check Jin Young's QR.

1343
00:55:06,800 --> 00:55:10,533
From what I've seen, you seemed
to take care of Jin Young a lot.

1344
00:55:11,600 --> 00:55:15,399
If I'd felt like
you were only taking care of me,

1345
00:55:15,400 --> 00:55:16,732
I think I would've
shown my feelings to you too.

1346
00:55:16,733 --> 00:55:19,832
I thought I approached you a lot
at the swimming pool.

1347
00:55:19,833 --> 00:55:21,199
I was the one who made
a lot of effort to get closer first.

1348
00:55:21,200 --> 00:55:23,199
I think I chose you
on the Love QR that day.

1349
00:55:23,200 --> 00:55:25,133
No, you chose Jun Han then.

1350
00:55:26,100 --> 00:55:27,833
- No.
- Yes.

1351
00:55:28,400 --> 00:55:31,032
That was the day
we played the Truth Card session...

1352
00:55:31,033 --> 00:55:32,232
after we came back from the pool.

1353
00:55:32,233 --> 00:55:33,933
And I kept choosing you
during the session.

1354
00:55:34,233 --> 00:55:37,666
That's true,
but you eventually sent the QR to Jun Han.

1355
00:55:37,900 --> 00:55:40,000
I just looked at your history.

1356
00:55:41,400 --> 00:55:42,765
I had to get to know other people too.

1357
00:55:42,766 --> 00:55:43,966
I said I'd let you know after that.

1358
00:55:45,366 --> 00:55:47,099
This is what makes me confused.

1359
00:55:47,100 --> 00:55:48,266
What will happen between these two?

1360
00:55:48,566 --> 00:55:50,866
But what I really don't understand is...

1361
00:55:51,666 --> 00:55:55,732
that Jun Han, Jin Woo, and even Yun So
all asked me the same thing.

1362
00:55:55,733 --> 00:56:01,266
They all asked, "Don't you like Jung Won?"

1363
00:56:01,866 --> 00:56:02,865
Was I the only one who couldn't tell?

1364
00:56:02,866 --> 00:56:04,932
Why was it so hard for me to notice?

1365
00:56:04,933 --> 00:56:07,133
They all came to me and asked that.

1366
00:56:07,733 --> 00:56:09,899
Everyone seemed to know,

1367
00:56:09,900 --> 00:56:11,902
to the point where I wondered
if I was making it too obvious.

1368
00:56:12,000 --> 00:56:14,332
I really didn't notice at all.

1369
00:56:14,333 --> 00:56:15,399
Maybe you just wanted
to pretend not to know?

1370
00:56:15,400 --> 00:56:18,932
No, absolutely not.
I really didn't notice.

1371
00:56:18,933 --> 00:56:20,377
I thought...

1372
00:56:21,144 --> 00:56:24,848
I was honest with you and showed
my feelings a lot at the amusement park.

1373
00:56:25,666 --> 00:56:28,332
- Was that not enough?
- No, today at the amusement park,

1374
00:56:28,333 --> 00:56:30,165
I saw how you expressed your feelings,

1375
00:56:30,166 --> 00:56:33,465
- I thought I expressed myself a lot.
- and I acknowledged it.

1376
00:56:33,466 --> 00:56:35,299
I admit that you expressed
your feelings a lot today.

1377
00:56:35,300 --> 00:56:37,066
- I really did express myself a lot today.
- Right.

1378
00:56:38,433 --> 00:56:42,132
And I'm also grateful
that you asked me to talk.

1379
00:56:42,133 --> 00:56:46,132
If you hadn't asked me to talk,

1380
00:56:46,133 --> 00:56:50,599
I might've just given up and thought,
"He must end up with Jin Young."

1381
00:56:50,600 --> 00:56:51,799
Exactly.

1382
00:56:51,800 --> 00:56:54,144
Right. If those two hadn't talked today,
who knows what would have happened?

1383
00:56:55,166 --> 00:56:56,600
So how do you feel now?

1384
00:56:57,300 --> 00:56:59,065
I'm sure now.

1385
00:56:59,066 --> 00:57:00,166
What are you sure about?

1386
00:57:01,433 --> 00:57:02,299
I'm diving in with you.

1387
00:57:02,300 --> 00:57:04,999
(Ji Hye is going to dive
right into Jung Won.)

1388
00:57:05,000 --> 00:57:06,733
- Is Ji Hye the only one who's sure?
- Unbelievable.

1389
00:57:08,533 --> 00:57:09,666
No more wandering.

1390
00:57:10,933 --> 00:57:15,399
I finally understand your feelings now.

1391
00:57:17,833 --> 00:57:19,400
I don't think I'll worry about it anymore.

1392
00:57:20,433 --> 00:57:22,100
Right. We only have two days left.

1393
00:57:23,200 --> 00:57:27,600
I think a lot of things will be sorted out
and changed in the next two days.

1394
00:57:29,033 --> 00:57:30,000
"Changed?"

1395
00:57:31,566 --> 00:57:33,433
Anything can change, of course.

1396
00:57:34,866 --> 00:57:35,933
Nothing is impossible.

1397
00:57:36,300 --> 00:57:37,466
But you shouldn't change.

1398
00:57:39,400 --> 00:57:40,600
I don't think I will.

1399
00:57:41,666 --> 00:57:43,100
You shouldn't.

1400
00:57:43,766 --> 00:57:47,232
(Jung Won doesn't leave a clear answer
to Ji Hye's confession.)

1401
00:57:47,233 --> 00:57:50,565
Even after Ji Hye lowered herself
this much...

1402
00:57:50,566 --> 00:57:52,532
and tried to explain her feelings,

1403
00:57:52,533 --> 00:57:54,499
he still isn't giving her a clear answer.

1404
00:57:54,500 --> 00:57:56,066
(Exactly.)

1405
00:57:56,966 --> 00:57:58,665
(Meanwhile, Ji Seung is still not sure
about opening the Pandora QR.)

1406
00:57:58,666 --> 00:58:02,133
I started wondering
if there is anyone here that you like.

1407
00:58:02,433 --> 00:58:03,299
Well...

1408
00:58:03,300 --> 00:58:04,133
Let me guess.

1409
00:58:04,866 --> 00:58:06,032
Go ahead.

1410
00:58:06,033 --> 00:58:07,099
Si Won.

1411
00:58:07,100 --> 00:58:08,599
- Actually...
- No?

1412
00:58:08,600 --> 00:58:09,899
Actually,

1413
00:58:09,900 --> 00:58:13,200
it's true that I chose Si Won a few times,

1414
00:58:16,266 --> 00:58:17,899
but I don't really know how he feels.

1415
00:58:17,900 --> 00:58:18,800
- You don't?
- No.

1416
00:58:19,966 --> 00:58:21,099
That's what I'm struggling with.

1417
00:58:21,100 --> 00:58:23,965
I just don't know
if he's worth checking his QR for.

1418
00:58:23,966 --> 00:58:25,865
- Let's go to the door and think about it.
- Hey!

1419
00:58:25,866 --> 00:58:27,599
Let's think about
whether you should open the door.

1420
00:58:27,600 --> 00:58:30,932
But I don't know if he is worthy enough
for me to check that QR.

1421
00:58:30,933 --> 00:58:33,499
But do you know what's funny?

1422
00:58:33,500 --> 00:58:35,732
I've kept choosing Si Won.

1423
00:58:35,733 --> 00:58:37,599
I think Si Won kept choosing me
in the beginning too.

1424
00:58:37,600 --> 00:58:38,932
But now I don't know anymore.

1425
00:58:38,933 --> 00:58:41,918
It started because he asked me out first,

1426
00:58:42,133 --> 00:58:45,165
and I think he is a really good person.
He is handsome too.

1427
00:58:45,166 --> 00:58:46,299
But the age...

1428
00:58:46,300 --> 00:58:48,232
- The gap is big, though.
- Right.

1429
00:58:48,233 --> 00:58:50,299
Still, he is really mature.

1430
00:58:50,300 --> 00:58:51,532
But there isn't much time left.

1431
00:58:51,533 --> 00:58:52,633
(The Pandora QR will close
in three minutes.)

1432
00:58:52,866 --> 00:58:54,633
Then should I just do it?

1433
00:58:55,033 --> 00:58:56,865
- Let's just do it.
- If I were you, I would do it.

1434
00:58:56,866 --> 00:58:59,733
Then half the responsibility is on you.

1435
00:59:00,000 --> 00:59:01,332
(She decides to open the Pandora QR.)

1436
00:59:01,333 --> 00:59:03,266
She must want to see it so badly.

1437
00:59:04,000 --> 00:59:06,233
She really wants to know,
but I think she is afraid.

1438
00:59:07,933 --> 00:59:08,700
Let's go.

1439
00:59:15,133 --> 00:59:19,199
(Si Won's No.1 choice every night)

1440
00:59:19,200 --> 00:59:20,699
(Day 1, Ji Seung)

1441
00:59:20,700 --> 00:59:21,832
(Day 2, Ji Seung)

1442
00:59:21,833 --> 00:59:24,199
(Day 3, Yu Jin)

1443
00:59:24,200 --> 00:59:26,299
(Day 4, Ji Seung)

1444
00:59:26,300 --> 00:59:27,700
Si Won chose Ji Seung again yesterday.

1445
00:59:28,100 --> 00:59:30,465
But the choice he made on Day 4
doesn't really mean much.

1446
00:59:30,466 --> 00:59:32,865
The same thing happened
to all the couples.

1447
00:59:32,866 --> 00:59:34,333
Today's dates were so intense
for everyone.

1448
00:59:35,433 --> 00:59:39,966
(Right after the ages were revealed,
Si Won sent his Love QR to Ji Seung.)

1449
00:59:41,284 --> 00:59:47,350
(But after that, Yu Jin and Si Won
had some time alone together.)

1450
00:59:48,100 --> 00:59:51,100
(Will Si Won's feelings
still be the same?)

1451
00:59:55,966 --> 00:59:56,999
Thank you for waiting.

1452
00:59:57,000 --> 00:59:59,300
- So, what do you say?
- What do I say?

1453
01:00:00,764 --> 01:00:01,664
(The QR Room closes after Ji Seung.)

1454
01:00:01,665 --> 01:00:03,799
Honestly, I'm not so sure about this.

1455
01:00:04,968 --> 01:00:05,936
Why aren't you going?

1456
01:00:06,270 --> 01:00:07,136
- Me?
- Yes.

1457
01:00:07,204 --> 01:00:09,805
I tend to live in the moment,

1458
01:00:10,517 --> 01:00:12,274
so I don't really care much
about the past.

1459
01:00:12,275 --> 01:00:13,709
- Exactly.
- That's a great mindset.

1460
01:00:13,734 --> 01:00:14,616
I was curious.

1461
01:00:14,641 --> 01:00:19,115
When things first started sparking
between you and Yu Jin?

1462
01:00:19,116 --> 01:00:20,584
I had absolutely no idea.

1463
01:00:20,817 --> 01:00:22,519
Well, when we went to the pool,

1464
01:00:22,719 --> 01:00:24,820
there were five of us in each car.

1465
01:00:24,998 --> 01:00:27,824
- Right, we were in different cars.
- Yes, and then after that,

1466
01:00:27,825 --> 01:00:29,631
we ended up sitting
right next to each other.

1467
01:00:30,127 --> 01:00:31,636
And our conversation
just flowed so smoothly.

1468
01:00:31,661 --> 01:00:32,427
True.

1469
01:00:32,428 --> 01:00:34,997
It was really fun talking to her.
Ever since then,

1470
01:00:35,399 --> 01:00:38,801
I wanted to sit down and have
a proper conversation with her.

1471
01:00:39,336 --> 01:00:42,338
And I feel like we've been
progressing step by step.

1472
01:00:43,440 --> 01:00:44,340
But then,

1473
01:00:44,674 --> 01:00:46,376
right before we finally got to talk,

1474
01:00:46,576 --> 01:00:48,812
we found out we have a 12-year age gap.

1475
01:00:49,246 --> 01:00:53,115
So things hadn't even started
at that point yesterday?

1476
01:00:53,216 --> 01:00:54,950
Right. Until our ages were revealed,

1477
01:00:54,951 --> 01:00:57,087
I hadn't really gotten a chance
to talk to her.

1478
01:00:57,254 --> 01:00:59,056
But after we found out,

1479
01:00:59,057 --> 01:01:00,724
we talked until very late at night.

1480
01:01:00,757 --> 01:01:03,025
And I really loved our conversation.

1481
01:01:03,193 --> 01:01:04,593
- Oh, they're coming.
- So...

1482
01:01:05,295 --> 01:01:07,796
So you wanted to talk to her
and see where things stand?

1483
01:01:07,797 --> 01:01:09,899
Going on a date is completely different
from just chatting.

1484
01:01:11,668 --> 01:01:12,769
Where did they go?

1485
01:01:13,437 --> 01:01:17,040
Why is everyone in such a rush
now that Pandora's QR is closed?

1486
01:01:17,750 --> 01:01:19,451
And our date today was really nice too.

1487
01:01:19,476 --> 01:01:20,976
So as of today, I'm locked in on her.

1488
01:01:20,977 --> 01:01:23,645
They are on completely different
wavelengths right now!

1489
01:01:23,646 --> 01:01:25,180
You know what's crazy?

1490
01:01:25,181 --> 01:01:27,883
As soon as I looked, it said,
"The QR Room is closed."

1491
01:01:28,819 --> 01:01:30,515
- Was it closed when you checked?
- Yes.

1492
01:01:30,720 --> 01:01:32,697
- It doesn't really matter to you, right?
- Actually, I'm glad.

1493
01:01:32,722 --> 01:01:33,924
Oh, you're happy about it?

1494
01:01:34,991 --> 01:01:35,824
Jin Young.

1495
01:01:36,259 --> 01:01:37,259
(Pointing)

1496
01:01:37,260 --> 01:01:37,960
What?

1497
01:01:38,829 --> 01:01:40,072
- Huh?
- Want to head outside?

1498
01:01:40,097 --> 01:01:42,164
Outside? Sure, let's go.

1499
01:01:43,066 --> 01:01:44,533
Did Jung Won and Ji Hye go somewhere?

1500
01:01:44,534 --> 01:01:46,169
- Huh?
- Did they go somewhere?

1501
01:01:46,903 --> 01:01:48,572
It's exactly what you think.

1502
01:01:50,607 --> 01:01:52,441
This is my only chance.

1503
01:01:52,442 --> 01:01:55,979
I don't want to take away
from your time with Jung Won.

1504
01:01:57,948 --> 01:01:59,582
You know, I'm a little tipsy.

1505
01:01:59,583 --> 01:02:00,917
More than I was earlier.

1506
01:02:01,785 --> 01:02:02,585
I like that.

1507
01:02:02,586 --> 01:02:03,920
- I'm way more drunk than before.
- He likes it.

1508
01:02:05,088 --> 01:02:06,855
Si Won looks uncomfortable.

1509
01:02:06,856 --> 01:02:08,190
This is funny.

1510
01:02:08,358 --> 01:02:09,091
Why?

1511
01:02:09,459 --> 01:02:10,793
- Nothing.
- Why is it funny?

1512
01:02:11,261 --> 01:02:12,962
It's just funny how we're all
splitting off in pairs.

1513
01:02:12,963 --> 01:02:13,829
I see.

1514
01:02:15,098 --> 01:02:17,866
(Ji Seung looks relieved
after checking the Pandora's QR.)

1515
01:02:18,335 --> 01:02:20,603
(Si Won looking at the photo
he took with Yu Jin)

1516
01:02:20,604 --> 01:02:22,705
He's looking at his photo with Yu Jin?

1517
01:02:23,006 --> 01:02:24,273
This is getting really interesting.

1518
01:02:24,574 --> 01:02:25,274
Is it?

1519
01:02:28,545 --> 01:02:33,816
(Awkward silence
after a brief conversation)

1520
01:02:34,284 --> 01:02:38,320
(Si Won looking at his photo
with Yu Jin again)

1521
01:02:42,192 --> 01:02:43,959
What on earth is going on here?

1522
01:02:44,694 --> 01:02:46,862
They're just staring straight ahead.

1523
01:02:47,130 --> 01:02:49,798
It's like they're in completely
different worlds.

1524
01:02:50,667 --> 01:02:54,670
(They sit in complete silence.)

1525
01:02:55,672 --> 01:02:56,739
I don't know, though.

1526
01:02:57,974 --> 01:02:58,740
What?

1527
01:03:02,612 --> 01:03:04,546
I think I'll head back to my room.
I don't really like it out here.

1528
01:03:04,547 --> 01:03:05,380
Let's head to our room.

1529
01:03:06,416 --> 01:03:07,484
"Let's head to our room?"

1530
01:03:07,584 --> 01:03:09,084
Or we can head back later.

1531
01:03:11,454 --> 01:03:12,688
(Si Won doesn't answer.)

1532
01:03:12,689 --> 01:03:14,690
Everyone else is chatting.

1533
01:03:15,492 --> 01:03:16,559
We can always meet back up later.

1534
01:03:16,560 --> 01:03:18,594
She practically invited him to her room,
but he's totally ignoring her.

1535
01:03:18,595 --> 01:03:20,796
(Si Won's silence continues.)

1536
01:03:20,931 --> 01:03:22,164
I think I'll head inside.

1537
01:03:22,165 --> 01:03:23,032
Okay.

1538
01:03:24,768 --> 01:03:29,038
(Ji Seung heads back alone.)

1539
01:03:29,773 --> 01:03:32,242
(Si Won is left alone
after rejecting Ji Seung's invitation.)

1540
01:03:32,243 --> 01:03:34,277
Si Won is so ruthless.

1541
01:03:34,678 --> 01:03:35,587
He's looking at the photo again.

1542
01:03:35,612 --> 01:03:36,946
He completely shut her down.

1543
01:03:37,380 --> 01:03:43,819
(Are his feelings for Ji Seung
completely gone?)

1544
01:03:45,689 --> 01:03:47,490
So, they're pairing up?

1545
01:03:47,491 --> 01:03:50,626
(Jin Young and Jin Woo head
to the Talk Room.)

1546
01:03:50,627 --> 01:03:52,629
We might have to pull an all-nighter.

1547
01:03:53,296 --> 01:03:55,264
(Ji Hye and Jung Won
step outside as well.)

1548
01:03:55,265 --> 01:03:56,399
Let's grab a drink!

1549
01:03:57,767 --> 01:03:59,000
What do you want to do? It's up to you.

1550
01:03:59,001 --> 01:04:00,268
- Me?
- Go talk to him if you want.

1551
01:04:00,269 --> 01:04:01,703
I think I'll talk to Jung Won a bit more.

1552
01:04:01,704 --> 01:04:03,438
- We're going to keep drinking.
- I see.

1553
01:04:03,974 --> 01:04:05,717
- Do whatever you want.
- Let's keep drinking.

1554
01:04:05,742 --> 01:04:06,475
Okay.

1555
01:04:07,143 --> 01:04:08,543
This is a great chance for Jin Young.

1556
01:04:08,544 --> 01:04:10,422
She hasn't really had a chance
to talk to him yet.

1557
01:04:11,014 --> 01:04:12,214
(Locking arms)

1558
01:04:12,215 --> 01:04:13,425
Are they locking arms?

1559
01:04:13,450 --> 01:04:14,216
Do whatever you want.

1560
01:04:14,217 --> 01:04:15,894
If you're not coming with me,
I'm going to sleep.

1561
01:04:15,919 --> 01:04:16,786
Really?

1562
01:04:17,153 --> 01:04:18,787
- Hey, Jung Won.
- Yes?

1563
01:04:19,422 --> 01:04:21,723
- Are you leaving?
- No.

1564
01:04:21,791 --> 01:04:23,026
Let's have a drink here.

1565
01:04:23,193 --> 01:04:23,926
Oh, really?

1566
01:04:24,427 --> 01:04:25,794
She wants some alone time with him.

1567
01:04:25,795 --> 01:04:26,561
Really?

1568
01:04:27,197 --> 01:04:28,097
Jin Woo!

1569
01:04:28,365 --> 01:04:29,398
Talk Room is right over there.

1570
01:04:29,399 --> 01:04:30,900
Okay. Is someone in there?

1571
01:04:31,201 --> 01:04:32,202
I don't think so.

1572
01:04:32,369 --> 01:04:34,203
- Jung Won, can I borrow a sheet mask?
- Yes, sure.

1573
01:04:34,228 --> 01:04:35,295
(Jin Woo gives Jin Young some space.)

1574
01:04:36,072 --> 01:04:38,907
(Ji Hye leaves as well.)

1575
01:04:39,376 --> 01:04:41,610
- Why do you look so upset?
- What? No, I'm not.

1576
01:04:41,978 --> 01:04:43,912
Why is your hair such a mess?

1577
01:04:43,913 --> 01:04:46,048
- Is it?
- What were you two doing in there?

1578
01:04:46,049 --> 01:04:48,517
Nothing. We didn't do anything.

1579
01:04:48,518 --> 01:04:50,786
- Nothing.
- You seem highly suspicious.

1580
01:04:50,787 --> 01:04:52,020
There's nothing to worry about.

1581
01:04:53,056 --> 01:04:54,890
The two of them...

1582
01:04:54,891 --> 01:04:57,159
need to clear up
all their misunderstandings right here.

1583
01:04:57,160 --> 01:04:58,093
(What will they talk about?)

1584
01:05:02,532 --> 01:05:03,800
Did you ever tell me?

1585
01:05:03,801 --> 01:05:06,435
Why you chose me on the third day?

1586
01:05:06,903 --> 01:05:08,170
No, I didn't tell you yet.

1587
01:05:08,405 --> 01:05:09,305
Tell me.

1588
01:05:09,406 --> 01:05:11,072
So, before that, I had chosen Ji Hye.

1589
01:05:11,073 --> 01:05:12,574
So why did I switch to you after that?

1590
01:05:12,809 --> 01:05:15,477
Nothing really happened between you
choosing Ji Hye and then me.

1591
01:05:15,979 --> 01:05:17,613
So why the sudden change of heart?

1592
01:05:17,614 --> 01:05:18,414
For me,

1593
01:05:19,516 --> 01:05:21,150
when you locked arms with me,

1594
01:05:21,151 --> 01:05:23,552
it made a huge impact.

1595
01:05:26,389 --> 01:05:28,223
Because I had been feeling really bad.

1596
01:05:28,224 --> 01:05:29,157
He felt so guilty.

1597
01:05:29,158 --> 01:05:32,527
I felt like I wasn't stepping up as a man.

1598
01:05:33,429 --> 01:05:35,732
I had asked to meet up and talk,

1599
01:05:36,066 --> 01:05:37,934
and I definitely could have made the time.

1600
01:05:38,702 --> 01:05:40,503
But I didn't,
and I felt terrible about it.

1601
01:05:40,603 --> 01:05:41,403
Right.

1602
01:05:42,272 --> 01:05:45,007
But despite all that,
in front of everyone,

1603
01:05:45,541 --> 01:05:47,329
you still came up and locked arms with me.

1604
01:05:47,644 --> 01:05:49,479
I had so much respect for you
for doing that.

1605
01:05:50,047 --> 01:05:52,849
And that was the moment
I found myself most attracted to you.

1606
01:05:54,684 --> 01:05:56,184
I see.

1607
01:05:57,220 --> 01:05:58,621
Now I have my answer.

1608
01:05:59,862 --> 01:06:01,462
Did you check my Pandora's QR?

1609
01:06:02,025 --> 01:06:03,325
Or someone else's?

1610
01:06:03,927 --> 01:06:04,827
Oh my gosh!

1611
01:06:05,028 --> 01:06:06,061
- The QR?
- Yes.

1612
01:06:06,663 --> 01:06:07,797
Whose do you think?

1613
01:06:08,264 --> 01:06:09,365
Mine, right?

1614
01:06:09,632 --> 01:06:10,799
(Awkward silence)

1615
01:06:10,800 --> 01:06:12,334
- Oh, no!
- It's a secret.

1616
01:06:12,335 --> 01:06:14,771
Why can't you just tell me?

1617
01:06:14,772 --> 01:06:17,471
Stay curious about me.

1618
01:06:17,741 --> 01:06:19,117
I'll tell you some other time.

1619
01:06:19,142 --> 01:06:20,909
- No, tell me now.
- No way.

1620
01:06:20,910 --> 01:06:23,678
- Why not?
- I want to keep you guessing.

1621
01:06:24,514 --> 01:06:25,914
Oh, come on.

1622
01:06:25,915 --> 01:06:27,149
I want to keep you curious.

1623
01:06:27,150 --> 01:06:28,685
Come on, you've already been caught.

1624
01:06:28,845 --> 01:06:30,445
You chose me.

1625
01:06:32,055 --> 01:06:33,655
- Oh, no.
- I don't know.

1626
01:06:38,661 --> 01:06:39,427
But...

1627
01:06:40,630 --> 01:06:42,432
why are you so sure about me?

1628
01:06:42,766 --> 01:06:44,333
What do you mean "sure?"

1629
01:06:44,334 --> 01:06:45,702
Are you not sure about me?

1630
01:06:45,770 --> 01:06:48,170
- Why do I like you?
- Yes.

1631
01:06:48,571 --> 01:06:50,106
Out of all these people here.

1632
01:06:51,374 --> 01:06:57,045
(Jin Young thinks deeply
about Jung Won's question.)

1633
01:06:58,214 --> 01:06:59,080
I think...

1634
01:07:00,083 --> 01:07:00,849
Well...

1635
01:07:01,351 --> 01:07:03,419
When I picture being with someone
in the real world...

1636
01:07:03,654 --> 01:07:05,354
and who fits into my life,

1637
01:07:06,289 --> 01:07:07,223
it was you.

1638
01:07:08,791 --> 01:07:11,860
I really like you right now.

1639
01:07:11,861 --> 01:07:12,895
But...

1640
01:07:13,563 --> 01:07:14,530
I don't know...

1641
01:07:14,531 --> 01:07:16,732
if it's just the excitement
of this environment,

1642
01:07:16,733 --> 01:07:20,769
or if we are actually compatible people...

1643
01:07:20,770 --> 01:07:23,572
who would work well in the long run.

1644
01:07:23,573 --> 01:07:26,041
I wanted to be sure about that.

1645
01:07:26,042 --> 01:07:28,378
Come on, I'm not just
some fleeting excitement.

1646
01:07:28,511 --> 01:07:29,479
I don't know.

1647
01:07:29,980 --> 01:07:31,681
I'm actually great in the long run.

1648
01:07:32,182 --> 01:07:33,315
Sell yourself to me then.

1649
01:07:33,384 --> 01:07:35,417
How should I win you over?

1650
01:07:35,418 --> 01:07:37,052
You'll find out soon enough
once we're out of here.

1651
01:07:37,053 --> 01:07:39,888
(Laughs)

1652
01:07:40,457 --> 01:07:41,991
Come here.

1653
01:07:42,459 --> 01:07:44,060
What did you and Ji Hye talk about?

1654
01:07:46,029 --> 01:07:47,262
What did you talk about with Ji Hye?

1655
01:07:47,263 --> 01:07:48,397
(Naturally holding hands)

1656
01:07:48,398 --> 01:07:49,064
They're holding hands.

1657
01:07:49,065 --> 01:07:50,175
What did you guys talk about?

1658
01:07:50,200 --> 01:07:51,333
How much do you want to know?

1659
01:07:51,334 --> 01:07:52,702
I'm dying to know. Tell me.

1660
01:07:52,703 --> 01:07:54,037
- Really?
- Tell me.

1661
01:08:01,744 --> 01:08:03,211
What is happening right now?

1662
01:08:03,212 --> 01:08:05,213
(What on earth is this timing?)

1663
01:08:05,448 --> 01:08:07,049
(Ji Hye suddenly enters the Talk Room.)

1664
01:08:07,450 --> 01:08:08,717
(Flustered)

1665
01:08:08,718 --> 01:08:09,961
Where did Jun Han go?

1666
01:08:09,986 --> 01:08:12,188
He was cooking in the common area earlier.

1667
01:08:13,323 --> 01:08:14,390
(Leaves)

1668
01:08:17,861 --> 01:08:19,963
She was so upset
she didn't even close the door.

1669
01:08:21,564 --> 01:08:23,932
What worries me about this is...

1670
01:08:24,767 --> 01:08:29,238
how deeply Jung Won was talking
to Ji Hye just a moment ago.

1671
01:08:29,339 --> 01:08:30,906
They had such a serious conversation.

1672
01:08:30,907 --> 01:08:32,741
But the second he walks out,

1673
01:08:32,809 --> 01:08:35,210
he starts acting like this with Jin Young.

1674
01:08:35,211 --> 01:08:37,312
- And Ji Hye saw the whole thing.
- Yes.

1675
01:08:37,415 --> 01:08:40,049
It's hard to look at Jung Won
in a good light right now.

1676
01:08:40,050 --> 01:08:41,986
This is going to be so tough on Ji Hye.

1677
01:08:41,987 --> 01:08:43,185
I think...

1678
01:08:43,487 --> 01:08:47,022
Jung Won needs to make up his mind
and stick with it.

1679
01:08:47,290 --> 01:08:50,059
He's playing the ultimate
wild card right now.

1680
01:08:50,927 --> 01:08:52,628
(What a massive curveball.)

1681
01:08:53,062 --> 01:08:53,930
With Ji Hye?

1682
01:08:54,597 --> 01:08:55,498
I just...

1683
01:08:56,699 --> 01:08:58,501
told her that I felt bad.

1684
01:08:59,469 --> 01:09:01,270
Okay, I won't pry any further.

1685
01:09:01,938 --> 01:09:03,940
Why? You can ask. It's fine.

1686
01:09:07,110 --> 01:09:09,045
So, how was your date with Jin Woo today?

1687
01:09:09,746 --> 01:09:10,746
Jin Woo?

1688
01:09:11,915 --> 01:09:14,083
He was flirting with me big time.

1689
01:09:14,084 --> 01:09:16,252
Really? And how did you react?

1690
01:09:16,553 --> 01:09:18,120
(Jung Won holds Jin Young's hand.)

1691
01:09:18,121 --> 01:09:19,088
See that?

1692
01:09:21,558 --> 01:09:22,424
For me,

1693
01:09:22,859 --> 01:09:24,994
I've already made up my mind
to go all-in on you.

1694
01:09:27,263 --> 01:09:28,063
Well, that's...

1695
01:09:28,230 --> 01:09:29,874
Why don't you waver just a little bit?

1696
01:09:29,899 --> 01:09:31,566
Even if you choose me in the end.

1697
01:09:31,702 --> 01:09:33,069
- Just to keep it fun.
- Should I?

1698
01:09:33,369 --> 01:09:34,936
(Look at this guy.)

1699
01:09:34,937 --> 01:09:36,538
Calm down. It's okay.

1700
01:09:37,740 --> 01:09:38,708
Control yourself.

1701
01:09:39,509 --> 01:09:40,510
We're the hosts.

1702
01:09:41,177 --> 01:09:41,943
Oh my gosh.

1703
01:09:42,354 --> 01:09:43,821
Why don't you waver just a little bit?

1704
01:09:43,846 --> 01:09:45,580
Even if you choose me in the end.

1705
01:09:45,915 --> 01:09:47,250
- Just to keep it fun.
- Should I?

1706
01:09:47,417 --> 01:09:48,784
And make you a little more nervous?

1707
01:09:48,785 --> 01:09:50,286
Yes, keep me on my toes.

1708
01:09:50,287 --> 01:09:52,822
You want me to make you nervous?
Is that what you want?

1709
01:09:52,923 --> 01:09:54,856
I can definitely do that.

1710
01:09:54,916 --> 01:09:58,086
What are your plans for tomorrow? Tell me.

1711
01:09:58,361 --> 01:09:59,529
- Tomorrow?
- Yes.

1712
01:09:59,864 --> 01:10:02,598
- Just sleep well.
- No way, don't give me that.

1713
01:10:03,466 --> 01:10:05,100
Act tough.

1714
01:10:05,566 --> 01:10:07,299
- Okay?
- How do I do that?

1715
01:10:07,300 --> 01:10:08,571
Act like a tough woman.

1716
01:10:08,766 --> 01:10:10,732
(Staring)

1717
01:10:10,733 --> 01:10:12,842
They look like they're about
to hug any second.

1718
01:10:13,700 --> 01:10:14,644
Okay?

1719
01:10:15,600 --> 01:10:16,699
You're so corny.

1720
01:10:16,700 --> 01:10:19,933
- Just act tough.
- You're suddenly being so corny.

1721
01:10:20,400 --> 01:10:21,965
You're sleepy, aren't you?

1722
01:10:21,966 --> 01:10:24,232
Aren't you? Be honest.

1723
01:10:25,100 --> 01:10:27,366
Jung Won is the ultimate king
of this jungle.

1724
01:10:28,833 --> 01:10:32,166
(Meanwhile,
Jun Han is in the common area.)

1725
01:10:32,666 --> 01:10:35,266
(Ji Hye comes to see Jun Han.)

1726
01:10:37,000 --> 01:10:38,366
- I'm here.
- Hey.

1727
01:10:39,666 --> 01:10:40,566
Here, eat this.

1728
01:10:40,800 --> 01:10:41,633
What did you make?

1729
01:10:41,800 --> 01:10:42,633
What's this?

1730
01:10:43,400 --> 01:10:44,807
What did you make this time?

1731
01:10:45,033 --> 01:10:46,075
Bean sprout soup.

1732
01:10:47,666 --> 01:10:49,212
You get pretty bad hangovers.

1733
01:10:49,633 --> 01:10:52,233
(During Jung Won and Ji Hye's
conversation a moment ago)

1734
01:10:52,400 --> 01:10:53,683
Wasn't it that day?

1735
01:10:55,566 --> 01:10:58,432
Can we talk for a bit after you're done?

1736
01:10:58,433 --> 01:10:59,600
Sure.

1737
01:11:00,366 --> 01:11:02,265
- I'll head over as soon as we're done.
- We'll keep it short.

1738
01:11:02,266 --> 01:11:03,065
Take your time.

1739
01:11:03,066 --> 01:11:05,033
I'll be waiting in the common area.

1740
01:11:06,500 --> 01:11:08,665
(Then he made
bean sprout soup for Ji Hye.)

1741
01:11:08,666 --> 01:11:10,967
Maybe this will be
the turning point for them.

1742
01:11:15,066 --> 01:11:15,900
Eat up.

1743
01:11:16,566 --> 01:11:18,033
Are you serious?

1744
01:11:18,666 --> 01:11:20,100
Is this actually happening?

1745
01:11:20,833 --> 01:11:22,378
Let's eat together. Come over here.

1746
01:11:23,233 --> 01:11:24,965
You seriously made this for me?

1747
01:11:24,966 --> 01:11:29,965
Ji Hye walks out completely upset
after checking the chat,

1748
01:11:29,966 --> 01:11:33,132
and Jun Han is waiting for her
with bean sprout soup?

1749
01:11:33,133 --> 01:11:34,624
This might actually make her think,

1750
01:11:34,766 --> 01:11:36,966
"Maybe he's the one."

1751
01:11:37,266 --> 01:11:39,929
- Life is all about timing.
- Time to change your pick.

1752
01:11:43,466 --> 01:11:44,734
It's my first time making this.

1753
01:11:44,833 --> 01:11:47,032
- My absolute first time.
- Really?

1754
01:11:47,033 --> 01:11:47,833
Yes.

1755
01:11:49,933 --> 01:11:50,873
I'm touched.

1756
01:11:52,066 --> 01:11:54,944
This is so cheesy that I'm actually
cringing and a bit embarrassed.

1757
01:11:56,200 --> 01:11:57,565
(Nervous)

1758
01:11:57,566 --> 01:11:59,549
Wait, is his hand shaking?

1759
01:11:59,966 --> 01:12:02,166
But I really wanted to tell you this.

1760
01:12:02,900 --> 01:12:04,987
I'm going to start wearing my heart
on my sleeve tomorrow.

1761
01:12:05,700 --> 01:12:06,889
I'm going all-in.

1762
01:12:07,100 --> 01:12:08,399
(That's cute.)

1763
01:12:08,400 --> 01:12:09,200
What?

1764
01:12:09,800 --> 01:12:13,465
I'll just cut to the chase.

1765
01:12:13,466 --> 01:12:15,765
I know you like getting straight
to the point.

1766
01:12:15,766 --> 01:12:17,432
I don't care about the process.

1767
01:12:17,433 --> 01:12:18,532
I'm all about results.

1768
01:12:18,533 --> 01:12:20,100
Right?

1769
01:12:21,300 --> 01:12:22,805
So I'm asking you for a chance.

1770
01:12:23,900 --> 01:12:25,308
A chance to show you how I feel.

1771
01:12:27,266 --> 01:12:28,100
Let's go!

1772
01:12:28,366 --> 01:12:29,200
Okay.

1773
01:12:30,000 --> 01:12:31,013
I get what you mean.

1774
01:12:31,466 --> 01:12:33,365
Speak of the devil.

1775
01:12:33,366 --> 01:12:34,866
- Who?
- Jung Won.

1776
01:12:35,966 --> 01:12:37,499
Drinking a lot, are we?

1777
01:12:37,500 --> 01:12:38,832
Why are you still up?

1778
01:12:38,833 --> 01:12:40,189
I was just about to go to bed.

1779
01:12:40,366 --> 01:12:41,766
Why the romantic look?

1780
01:12:42,133 --> 01:12:44,832
I've decided to go all-in.

1781
01:12:44,833 --> 01:12:47,266
(Bursts out laughing at Jun Han's comment)

1782
01:12:47,500 --> 01:12:50,732
You've said that so many times already.

1783
01:12:50,733 --> 01:12:53,665
How many all-ins do you have left?

1784
01:12:53,666 --> 01:12:56,199
Seriously, you keep saying that.

1785
01:12:56,200 --> 01:12:59,065
No one is going to take him
seriously anymore.

1786
01:12:59,066 --> 01:13:00,966
I'm really going to prove it
starting tomorrow.

1787
01:13:01,733 --> 01:13:03,713
- It's not like the other...
- Did he say this multiple times?

1788
01:13:04,100 --> 01:13:05,899
Has he done this before?

1789
01:13:05,900 --> 01:13:08,699
Oh, no. That totally ruined the mood.

1790
01:13:08,700 --> 01:13:10,499
No, that's not...

1791
01:13:10,500 --> 01:13:11,921
Are you really that shallow?

1792
01:13:12,500 --> 01:13:13,865
No, I told you...

1793
01:13:13,866 --> 01:13:15,299
You're so funny.

1794
01:13:15,300 --> 01:13:17,199
I'm just...

1795
01:13:17,224 --> 01:13:19,152
Whatever. I'll just say it.

1796
01:13:20,100 --> 01:13:23,232
Everyone thinks I flirt with everyone,

1797
01:13:23,233 --> 01:13:25,468
so I'm just going to lay it all out here.

1798
01:13:26,266 --> 01:13:29,500
Whenever I open up, I always get rejected.

1799
01:13:30,666 --> 01:13:32,065
I see.

1800
01:13:32,066 --> 01:13:34,566
I actually chose Jun Han that time.

1801
01:13:35,133 --> 01:13:36,100
And...

1802
01:13:36,533 --> 01:13:40,466
I thought you were already taken.

1803
01:13:41,266 --> 01:13:43,500
You thought I was already taken?

1804
01:13:44,109 --> 01:13:45,665
That's what I thought.

1805
01:13:45,666 --> 01:13:48,032
- So I was just happy we got to talk.
- But he didn't know that.

1806
01:13:48,033 --> 01:13:48,865
Didn't know what?

1807
01:13:48,866 --> 01:13:50,275
That it was him and me.

1808
01:13:50,300 --> 01:13:51,066
Me?

1809
01:13:51,400 --> 01:13:52,732
Why are you pointing at me?

1810
01:13:52,733 --> 01:13:56,132
There is no way Jung Won
didn't know how you felt.

1811
01:13:56,133 --> 01:13:57,199
- If he's claiming...
- He said he didn't.

1812
01:13:57,200 --> 01:13:58,632
Then he's a total player.

1813
01:13:58,633 --> 01:14:01,166
(It's finally happening.)

1814
01:14:01,400 --> 01:14:02,900
Jun Han!

1815
01:14:03,233 --> 01:14:04,699
Then he's a total player.

1816
01:14:04,700 --> 01:14:06,865
What do you mean, a player?

1817
01:14:06,866 --> 01:14:11,099
If you're saying you didn't know
even after the Truth or Dare...

1818
01:14:11,100 --> 01:14:11,932
So I told him,

1819
01:14:11,933 --> 01:14:15,399
"How could you not know
when literally everyone else did?"

1820
01:14:15,400 --> 01:14:17,499
Didn't know what?

1821
01:14:17,500 --> 01:14:19,565
- I have no idea.
- What is it?

1822
01:14:19,566 --> 01:14:20,699
I don't know.

1823
01:14:20,700 --> 01:14:23,565
- They just went straight at him.
- Exactly!

1824
01:14:23,566 --> 01:14:26,799
I never got a real chance to approach you,

1825
01:14:26,800 --> 01:14:30,065
so I wanted to try at least once.

1826
01:14:30,066 --> 01:14:31,632
Jun Han really opened the floodgates.

1827
01:14:31,633 --> 01:14:34,832
I'll say it right in front of Jung Won.

1828
01:14:34,833 --> 01:14:36,832
Why do you keep dragging me into this?

1829
01:14:36,833 --> 01:14:38,365
I have no idea what's going on
between you two.

1830
01:14:38,366 --> 01:14:40,299
You guys were talking, so...

1831
01:14:40,300 --> 01:14:41,377
Why are you doing this to me?

1832
01:14:41,433 --> 01:14:43,999
You're free to go on dates with Jung Won,

1833
01:14:44,000 --> 01:14:46,532
but I'm just asking you
to give me a chance too.

1834
01:14:46,533 --> 01:14:48,117
Just a little bit of your time.

1835
01:14:48,900 --> 01:14:50,365
Okay.

1836
01:14:53,133 --> 01:14:55,725
I said this right in front of him
so you know I'm sincere.

1837
01:14:55,966 --> 01:14:56,799
I was being honest.

1838
01:14:56,800 --> 01:14:58,728
You really laid your cards on the table.

1839
01:15:00,600 --> 01:15:02,400
He really shook things up.

1840
01:15:02,733 --> 01:15:06,033
A battle between an open book
and a mystery man.

1841
01:15:06,633 --> 01:15:08,299
(What will happen to these four?)

1842
01:15:08,300 --> 01:15:09,200
What now?

1843
01:15:11,033 --> 01:15:13,300
"Check your date partner for today."

1844
01:15:13,900 --> 01:15:14,790
I think...

1845
01:15:14,814 --> 01:15:16,712
I wanted to be sure.

1846
01:15:16,726 --> 01:15:19,108
(Day-drinking date decided
by the older women)

1847
01:15:19,133 --> 01:15:22,265
You don't have any other guys
you want to talk to, right?

1848
01:15:22,266 --> 01:15:23,819
What about you? What do you want to do?

1849
01:15:24,066 --> 01:15:27,533
I think I'm going to focus entirely
on the girl I'm interested in.

1850
01:15:27,866 --> 01:15:29,265
Where are you coming from?

1851
01:15:29,266 --> 01:15:30,600
(Happy to see him)

1852
01:15:30,733 --> 01:15:32,094
I was so happy to see you.

1853
01:15:32,233 --> 01:15:33,865
I should just sleep out here tonight.

1854
01:15:33,866 --> 01:15:35,299
I'll stay with you.

1855
01:15:35,300 --> 01:15:36,600
(Blushing)

1856
01:15:36,933 --> 01:15:37,967
Have you made your choice?

1857
01:15:38,533 --> 01:15:39,835
I'm still figuring it out.

1858
01:15:40,200 --> 01:15:41,566
You need to reassure me.

1859
01:15:42,366 --> 01:15:43,166
I will.

1860
01:15:44,000 --> 01:15:45,307
I wanted you to be here...

1861
01:15:45,466 --> 01:15:46,509
and you actually were.

1862
01:15:47,466 --> 01:15:49,008
Was there something you wanted to ask me?

1863
01:15:49,033 --> 01:15:50,866
(Hesitating)

1864
01:15:51,066 --> 01:15:53,733
- It's hard to say.
- Is it?

1865
01:15:54,266 --> 01:15:58,032
It feels like you're in a rush...

1866
01:15:58,033 --> 01:16:00,632
to get married right now.

1867
01:16:00,633 --> 01:16:01,865
Really?

1868
01:16:01,866 --> 01:16:03,466
I'm not in a rush.

1869
01:16:05,300 --> 01:16:07,465
I just want to date someone...

1870
01:16:07,466 --> 01:16:09,133
with marriage in mind.

1871
01:16:11,266 --> 01:16:12,800
(Sighing)

1872
01:16:13,133 --> 01:16:17,999
It felt like he was
under a lot of pressure.

1873
01:16:18,000 --> 01:16:20,099
After talking with Ji Hye today,

1874
01:16:20,100 --> 01:16:21,444
I'm having second thoughts.

1875
01:16:22,033 --> 01:16:23,800
(Sigh)

1876
01:16:24,266 --> 01:16:27,566
I don't think there was anything
I could have done.

1877
01:16:30,066 --> 01:16:31,766
(Sigh)

1878
01:16:34,166 --> 01:16:34,966
Jin Young.

1879
01:16:36,000 --> 01:16:36,833
Do you want to talk?

1880
01:16:37,366 --> 01:16:39,199
You have terrible taste in men.

1881
01:16:39,200 --> 01:16:40,632
(Sighing)

1882
01:16:40,633 --> 01:16:43,599
Why do you even care about someone
who only makes you cry?

1883
01:16:43,600 --> 01:16:45,665
Why are you being so nice to me?

1884
01:16:45,666 --> 01:16:46,566
Just use me.

1885
01:16:46,800 --> 01:16:48,108
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)

1886
01:16:48,133 --> 01:16:50,499
Use me to take out your anger.

1887
01:16:50,500 --> 01:16:52,766
(How will the tangled love lines
at Yeon House play out?)
